%20have%20so%20far%20been%20recovered%20in%20the%20ongoing%20raids%20by%20Pune%20Police%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20police%20said%20that%20they%20unearthed%20a%20staggering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmeow-meow-drug-worth-rs-2-500-crore-found-in-delhi-pune-raids-5097966%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C100%20kilograms%20of%20mephedrone%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20an%20estimated%20value%20exceeding%20Rs%202%2C500%20crore%20in%20raids%20across%20Pune%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20began%20with%20the%20arrest%20of%20three%20drug%20smugglers%20in%20Pune%2C%20accompanied%20by%20the%20seizure%20of%20700%20kg%20of%20mephedrone.%20The%20subsequent%20interrogation%20of%20these%20individuals%20led%20to%20the%20confiscation%20of%20an%20additional%20400%20kg%20of%20the%20synthetic%20stimulant%20from%20godown-like%20structures%20in%20Delhi's%20Hauz%20Khas%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20large%20consignment%20of%20Mephedrone%20was%20stored%20in%20Pune%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20Kurkumbh%20MIDC%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Pune%20Police%20sources%2C%20the%20case%20will%20now%20be%20investigated%20from%20the%20terror%20funding%20angle.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708577820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Ftju10cio_mephedrone-drug_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-3-700-crore-worth-meow-meow-drugs-seized-in-a-week-as-maharashtra-raids-continue-5104580%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Banned%20drug%20mephedrone%20worth%20Rs%20300%20crore%20has%20been%20seized%20during%20a%20raid%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sangli%2C%20officials%20said%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-3-700-crore-worth-meow-meow-drugs-seized-in-a-week-as-maharashtra-raids-continue-5104580%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-3-700-crore-worth-meow-meow-drugs-seized-in-a-week-as-maharashtra-raids-continue-5104580%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-3-700-crore-worth-meow-meow-drugs-seized-in-a-week-as-maharashtra-raids-continue-5104580%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20%26quot%3BResearch%20Vessel%26quot%3B%20Set%20To%20Dock%20In%20Male%20Amid%20India-Maldives%20Tensions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAmid%20strained%20ties%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Maldives%2C%20a%20Chinese%20vessel%20has%20entered%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20island%20nation%20and%20is%20set%20to%20dock%20in%20its%20capital%20Male.%20The%204%2C300-ton%20Xiang%20Yang%20Hong%2003%20is%20classified%20as%20a%20'research'%20vessel%20mapping%20the%20floor%20of%20Indian%20Ocean.%20The%20Indian%20Navy%20has%20pointed%20out%20that%20mapping%20of%20the%20seabed%20can%20enable%20submarine%20operations%20in%20the%20geopolitically-significant%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vessel%20belongs%20to%20the%20Third%20Institute%20of%20Oceanography%20in%20China.%20Its%20purported%20objectives%20are%20seabed%20mapping%20and%20mineral%20exploration%2C%20among%20others.%20The%20vessel%20sailed%20from%20Sanya%20in%20China%20over%20a%20month%20ago%20and%20is%20likely%20to%20dock%20in%20Male%20shortly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20last%20month%20said%20the%20Chinese%20ship%20will%20not%20conduct%20any%20research%20in%20its%20waters%20but%20will%20only%20come%20for%20%26quot%3Brotation%20and%20replenishment%26quot%3B.%20India's%20concerns%2C%20however%2C%20are%20not%20limited%20to%20the%20waters%20of%20the%20Maldives.%20They%20extend%20to%20the%20other%20areas%20this%20vessel%20is%20operating%20in.%20This%20ship%20has%20been%20moving%20in%20the%20waters%20between%20the%20Maldives%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20a%20zigzag%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavy%20Chief%20Admiral%20R%20Kumar%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20interview%20last%20week%20that%20charting%20underwater%20regions%20''may%20have%20military%20applications%20as%20well%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20ability%20to%20deploy%20submarines%20or%20operate%20submarines.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi%20is%20watching%20the%20ship's%20movements%20with%20concerns%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20China's%20expanding%20influence%20in%20the%20Indian%20Ocean%20Region%20and%20the%20frost%20in%20India-Maldives%20relations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENew%20Delhi's%20ties%20with%20Male%20have%20touched%20an%20all-time%20low%20since%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20took%20over%20as%20President%20late%20last%20year.%20Soon%20after%20his%20election%2C%20Muizzu%20moved%20to%20remove%20Indian%20troops%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20for%20humanitarian%20activities%20and%20medical%20evacuation.%20He%20also%20visited%20Beijing%20and%20met%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%20Once%20back%2C%20the%20Maldives%20president%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20may%20be%20small%2C%20but%20this%20doesn't%20give%20them%20the%20licence%20to%20bully%20us.%26quot%3B%20The%20remark%2C%20which%20did%20not%20name%20any%20country%2C%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20swipe%20at%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20two%20sides%20had%20reached%20an%20agreement%20on%20withdrawing%20Indian%20troops%20by%20May.%20The%20External%20Affairs%20Ministry%20has%20said%20they%20had%20%26quot%3Bagreed%20on%20a%20set%20of%20mutually%20workable%20solutions%20to%20enable%20continued%20operation%20of%20Indian%20aviation%20platforms%26quot%3B%20that%20provide%20humanitarian%20services%20to%20the%20Maldives.%20The%20soldiers%2C%20reports%20said%2C%20would%20now%20be%20replaced%20by%20civilians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Maldives%20President's%20anti-India%20stand%20has%20also%20led%20to%20domestic%20challenges.%20Several%20Maldivian%20opposition%20leaders%20have%20criticised%20the%20island%20nation's%20government%20o