%20the%20night.%20Considering%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20(Gujarat)%20high%20court%20and%20its%20fear%2C%20we%20definitely%20got%20the%20sound%20(of%20music)%20decreased%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20because%20Navratri%20could%20be%20allowed%20till%20late%20night%2C%20it%20brought%20Diwali%20to%20numerous%20households.%20To%20get%20a%20figure%20of%20that%20(how%20many%20households)%2C%20one%20needs%20to%20ask%20the%20poor%2C%20the%20vendors%20and%20those%20running%20small%20restaurants%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20continued.%20%E2%80%9CI%20made%20a%20statement%20(then)%20that%20if%20the%20people%20of%20my%20state%20cannot%20perform%20garba%20then%20would%20they%20do%20so%20in%20Pakistan%3F%20The%20very%20next%20day%20of%20this%20statement%2C%20people%20from%20a%20party%20(moved)%20a%20PIL%20in%20the%20HC.%20They%20have%20a%20problem%20if%20people%20of%20the%20state%20perform%20garba%20till%20late%20in%20the%20night.%20Can%E2%80%99t%20people%20perform%20garba%20till%20late%3F%20We%20had%20to%20face%20that%20situation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fin-selective-demolition-muslim-structures-razed-but-temple-spared-in-gujarats-dwarka%5C%22%3Ehas%20reported%20in%20the%20past%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20Sanghavi%20and%20Patel%E2%80%99s%20eagerness%20to%20raze%20Muslim%20structures%20%E2%80%93%20while%20seemingly%20ignoring%20Hindu%20ones%20that%20violate%20the%20same%20encroachment%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708577264000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fgujarat-home-minister-brags-about-demolishing-108-mazars-says-states-bulldozer-is-everywhere%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNow%2C%20Dada%E2%80%99s%20%5BBhupendra%20Patel's%5D%20bulldozer%20is%20moving%20around%20in%20every%20nook%20and%20corner%20of%20the%20state%20so%20that%20no%20temple%20or%20devsthan%20can%20be%20removed%20while%20hatching%2