www.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Fstock-market-live-updates-feb-22-sensex-nifty-sugar-eureka-forbes-zee-124022200070_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Why%20Court%20Said%20No%20Case%20Against%20US%20Cop%20Who%20Killed%20Indian%20Student%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJaahnavi%20Kandula%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20Indian%20student%2C%20was%20killed%20after%20being%20hit%20by%20a%20speeding%20police%20vehicle%20in%20the%20US%20state%20of%20Washington%20on%20January%2023%20last%20year.%20After%20a%20year%20of%20legal%20battles%2C%20court%20proceedings%2C%20statements%20from%20both%20the%20Indian%20and%20US%20governments%2C%20and%20calls%20for%20accountability%2C%20the%20police%20officer%20behind%20the%20wheels%20of%20the%20vehicle%20that%20ran%20over%20Ms%20Kandula%20will%20walk%20free%2C%20at%20least%20for%20now.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20acknowledging%20the%20impact%20on%20communities%20both%20locally%20and%20%26quot%3Bacross%20the%20world%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20US%20prosecutor%20claimed%20a%20lack%20of%20%26quot%3Bsufficient%20evidence%26quot%3B%20to%20pursue%20criminal%20charges%20against%20Seattle%20police%20officer%20Kevin%20Dave%2C%20who%20was%20driving%20at%20120%20kmph%20when%20his%20cop%20car%20hit%20Ms%20Kandula%2C%20a%20Master's%20student%20in%20Seattle%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20bodycam%20footage%20released%20by%20Seattle%20Police%2C%20officer%20Daniel%20Auderer%2C%20who%20was%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20collision%20but%20was%20present%20at%20the%20scene%2C%20callously%20laughed%20about%20the%20deadly%20crash%20before%20dismissing%20the%20need%20for%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20and%20making%20insensitive%20comments%20about%20Ms%20Kandula's%20age%20and%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EProsecutor's%20Decision%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKing%20County%20Prosecuting%20Attorney%20Leesa%20Manion%20expressed%20her%20concerns%20about%20Auderer's%20comments%2C%20calling%20them%20%26quot%3Bappalling%20and%20deeply%20troubling.%26quot%3B%20However%2C%20she%20added%20that%20as%20egregious%20as%20Auderer's%20remarks%20were%2C%20they%20do%20not%20alter%20the%20legal%20analysis%20of%20Dave's%20conduct.%20Instead%2C%20it%20falls%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%20(OPA)%20to%20address%20Auderer's%20unprofessional%20behavior.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuderer%2C%20who%20was%20pulled%20from%20patrol%20in%20September%202023%20and%20reassigned%20to%20a%20%26quot%3Bnon-operational%20position%2C%26quot%3B%20now%20faces%20potential%20termination%20pending%20a%20disciplinary%20hearing%20scheduled%20for%20March%204.%20The%20video%20of%20Auderer%20callously%20discussing%20Kandula's%20death%20has%20not%20only%20added%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire%20but%20has%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20culture%20within%20Seattle%20Police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShe%20was%2026%20anyway%2C%26quot%3B%20Auderer%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20limited%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeattle%20local%20media%20reported%20that%20speed%20was%20the%20primary%20cause%20of%20the%20collision%2C%20as%20Dave's%20high-speed%20response%20did%20not%20provide%20sufficient%20time%20for%20Ms%20Kandula%20to%20detect%2C%20address%2C%20and%20avoid%20the%20impending%20hazard.%20The%20officer%20did%20not%20have%20his%20siren%20continuously%20activated%2C%20instead%20opting%20to%20%26quot%3Bchirp%26quot%3B%20it%20at%20the%20intersection.%20While%20his%20emergency%20lights%20were%20on%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20a%20continuous%20siren%20and%20the%20excessive%20speed%20raised%20critical%20questions%20about%20the%20urgency%20and%20necessity%20of%20such%20a%20high-speed%20response.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memo%20to%20Seattle%20Police%2C%20prosecutors%20argued%20that%20there%20was%20not%20enough%20evidence%20to%20prove%20Dave%20showed%20a%20%26quot%3Bconscious%20disregard%20for%20others'%20safety.%26quot%3B%20The%20decision%20not%20to%20press%20criminal%20charges%20hinges%20on%20Washington%20State%20law's%20requirement%20to%20prove%20a%20case%20beyond%20any%20reasonable%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ECommunity%20Police%20Commission's%20Response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Community%20Police%20Commission%20(CPC)%20responded%20to%20the%20decision%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.seattle.gov%2Fdocuments%2FDepartments%2FCommunityPoliceCommission%2FPress%2520Releases%2F2024%2FCPC%2520statement%2520re%2520Officer%2520Kevin%2520Dave%2520022124.pdf%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20expressing%20condolences%20to%20Kandula's%20family%20and%20the%20Indian%20American%20community.%20The%20CPC%20acknowledged%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20legal%20standard%20applied%20to%20Dave's%20conduct%20and%20questioned%20at%20what%20speed%20his%20emergency%20response%20would%20be%20deemed%20reckless%20or%20disregarding%20the%20safety%20of%20pedestrians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20Officer%20Dave%20was%20traveling%2074%20mph%20on%20Dexter%20Avenue%20North%20at%20night%20prior%20to%20striking%20Ms%20Kandula%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20determined%20his%20conduct%20did%20not%20meet%20the%20legal%20standard%20of%20'recklessness'%20or%20'disregard%20for%20the%20safety%20of%20others'%20under%20Washington's%20vehicular%20homicide%20statute.%20It%20begs%20the%20question%3A%20at%20what%20speed%20would%20Officer%20Dave%20have%20had%20to%20drive%20for%20his%20emergency%20response%20to%20be%20considered%20reckless%20or%20disregarding%20the%20safety%20of%20pedestrians%20in%20the%20area%3F%26quot%3B%20a%20CPC%20statement%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CPC%20said%20it%20is%20working%20with%20Seattle%20Police%20regarding%20necessary%20changes%20to%20their%20emergency%20vehicle%20operation%20policy.%20The%20CPC%20demanded%20the%20need%20for%20policies%20that%20prioritise%20life%20and%20avoid%20putting%20the%20community%20at%20further%20risk.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20CPC%20is%20investigating%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20practice%20of%20responding%20to%20Seattle%20Fire%20Department%20calls%20for%20drug%20overdoses%2C%20seeking%20answers%20to%20why%20Dave%20was%20responding%20to%20such%20a%20call%20in%20the%20first%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EInternational%20Outrage%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20release%20of%20bodycam%20footage%20featuring%20Auderer's%20remarks%20triggered%20international%20outrage.%20Lawmakers%2C%20both%20in%20the%20United%20States%20and%20among%20the%20Indian-American%20community%2C%20condemned%20the%20behavior%20displayed%20in%20the%20video.%20Indian-American%20Congressman%20Ro%20Khanna%20expressed%20his%20dismay%2C%20stating%20that%20every%20Indian%20immigrant's%20life%20has%20infinite%20value%2C%20and%20anyone%20thinking%20otherwise%20should%20not%20be%20in%20law%20enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian-American%20Congresswoman%20Pramila%20Jayapal%20echoed%20the%20sentiment%2C%20calling%20the%20video%20appalling%20and%20demanding%20justice%20for%20Ms%20Kandula's%20family.%20The%20Consulate%20General%20of%20India%20in%20San%20Francisco%20raised%20concerns%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20seeking%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20and%20action%20against%20those%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20assured%20India%20of%20a%20quick%20and%20fair%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeattle%20City%20Mayor%20Bruce%20Harrell%2C%20in%20a%20letter%20to%20the%20Kandula%20family%2C%20sought%20to%20distance%20the%20city%20from%20Auderer's%20comments%2C%20stating%20that%20they%20do%20not%20reflect%20the%20feelings%20of%20the%20city%20or%20its%20communities.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708576140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2cnth4vg_jaahnavi-kandula-_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fno-criminal-case-against-us-cop-who-killed-indian-while-driving-at-120-kmph-5