to%20new%20highs%20by%20the%20end%20of%20June%20and%20gain%20nearly%209%25%20in%202024%2C%20despite%20already%20lofty%20valuations%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20polled%20by%20Reuters%2C%20who%20said%20a%20correction%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%20was%20unlikely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSE%20Sensex%20index%2C%20closely%20tracking%20the%20U.S.%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20index%2C%20climbed%20nearly%2019%25%20last%20year%20on%20expectations%20global%20central%20banks%20will%20cut%20interest%20rates%20in%202024%20and%20India's%20economic%20growth%20will%20outpace%20its%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBreaching%20the%2073%2C000%20mark%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%20January%2C%20the%20benchmark%20index%20is%20up%20over%201%25%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20is%20despite%20fading%20speculation%20about%20early%20rate%20cuts%20from%20the%20U.S.%20Federal%20Reserve%20triggering%20foreign%20portfolio%20outflows%20from%20many%20emerging%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOptimism%20in%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20also%20been%20driven%20by%20expectations%20the%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20will%20retain%20power%20in%20the%20upcoming%20national%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Feb.%2012-21%20Reuters%20poll%20of%2028%20equity%20analysts%20forecast%20the%20Sensex%20index%20would%20add%20another%204%25%20to%20reach%20a%20high%20of%2076%2C000%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%2C%20far%20above%20the%2070%2C000%20level%20expected%20in%20a%20November%20poll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20Tuesday's%20close%20of%2073%2C057%2C%20the%20BSE%20index%20is%20forecast%20to%20rise%207.5%25%20to%2078%2C550%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20That%20would%20be%20around%20a%209%25%20gain%20for%20the%20entire%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Indian%20economy%20remains%20a%20'star%20performing'%20economy%20against%20other%20emerging%20markets.%20Moreover%2C%20we%20firmly%20believe%20it%20will%20likely%20continue%20its%20growth%20momentum%20in%202024%20and%20remain%20the%20land%20of%20stability%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20a%20volatile%20global%20economy%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Neeraj%20Chadawar%2C%20head%20of%20quantitative%20equity%20research%20at%20Axis%20Securities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20entire%20setup%20for%20the%20market%20is%20very%20constructive%20at%20this%20level%20because%20the%20market%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20policy%20continuity%20in%20the%20upcoming%20national%20level%20election.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%2C%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economy%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20expand%20nearly%207%25%20this%20fiscal%20year%20and%20grow%20over%206%25%20in%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20but%20one%20of%20the%2026%20respondents%20to%20an%20additional%20question%20said%20corporate%20earnings%20would%20increase%20over%20the%20coming%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20probability%20of%20a%20market%20correction%20over%20the%20coming%20three%20months%2C%20a%20near%2060%25%20majority%20of%20respondents%2C%2016%20of%2027%20said%20it%20was%20unlikely%2C%20including%20two%20who%20said%20highly%20unlikely.%20Nine%20said%20likely%20and%20two%20said%20highly%20likely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20very%20difficult%20to%20call%20whether%20there%20is%20a%20major%20correction.%20But%20right%20now%20I%20think%20India%20is%20in%20a%20good%20macro%20situation%20and%20the%20concerns%20are%20more%20around%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20high%20valuations%20than%20anything%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Rajat%20Agarwal%2C%20Asia%20equity%20strategist%20at%20Societe%20Generale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20price-to-earnings%20ratio%20of%2024%2C%20the%20BSE%20index%20is%20trading%20above%20its%20long-term%20average%20of%2020%2C%20suggesting%20any%20further%20rise%20will%20only%20add%20to%20concerns%20around%20valuations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Nifty%2050%20index%20is%20forecast%20in%20the%20poll%20to%20gain%20over%202%25%20from%20Tuesday's%20close%20to%2022%2C750%20at%20the%20end%20of%20June%20and%2023%2C925%20at%20the%20end%20of%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708572240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2F2ln00a28_bombay-stock-exchange-bse-building-mumbai-reuters_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-index-to-rise-about-9-in-2024-correction-unlikely-report-5104041%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stock%20market%20will%20surge%20to%20new%20highs%20by%20the%20end%20of%20June%20and%20gain%20nearly%209%25%20in%202024%2C%20despite%20already%20lofty%20valuations%2C%20according%20to%20analysts%20polled%20by%20Reuters%2C%20who%20said%20a%20correction%20in%20the%20next%20three%20months%20was%20unlikely.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-index-to-rise-about-9-in-2024-correction-unlikely-report-5104041%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-index-to-rise-about-9-in-2024-correction-unlikely-report-5104041%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Fstock-index-to-rise-about-9-in-2024-correction-unlikely-report-5104041%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harry%20Styles'%20Alleged%20Stalker%20Accused%20Of%20Sending%20Singer%208%2C000%20Letters%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%2035-year-old%20woman%20from%20Brazil%20has%20been%20accused%20of%20stalking%20singer%20Harry%20Styles.%20Myra%20Carvalho%20has%20appeared%20in%20UK%20court%20after%20she%20sent%208%2C000%20handwritten%20letters%20to%20the%20singer%20in%20less%20than%20a%20month.%20The%20woman%20allegedly%20sent%20the%2030-year-old%20singer%20letters%20while%20in%20the%20UK%20and%20ordered%20a%20series%20of%20cards%20for%20him%20online%20which%20were%20sent%20to%20his%20address.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%