n%3Cp%3EAmid%20outrage%20over%20the%20insensitive%20remarks%2C%20he%20was%20pulled%20off%20patrol%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EDaniel%20Auderer's%20clarification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-death-without-context-us-cop-who-was-joking-about-indian-students-death-4394650%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDaniel%20Auderer%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0later%20said%20that%20he%20intended%20the%20comment%20as%20a%20mockery%20of%20lawyers.%20In%20a%20letter%20dated%20to%20the%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%2C%20Auderer%20reportedly%20said%20he%20laughed%20at%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20how%20these%20incidents%20are%20litigated%20and%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20how%20he%20has%20watched%20these%20incidents%20play%20out%20as%20two%20parties%20bargain%20over%20a%20tragedy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20time%20I%20believed%20the%20conversation%20was%20private%20and%20not%20being%20recorded.%20The%20conversation%20was%20also%20not%20within%20the%20course%20of%20my%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20letter%20to%20Gino%20Betts%2C%20director%20Office%20of%20Police%20Accountability%2C%20the%20news%20agency%20PTI%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20en%20route%20home%2C%20I%20called%20Mike%20Solan%20to%20give%20him%20an%20update%20regarding%20what%20had%20occurred.%20The%20phone%20call%20was%20inadvertently%20recorded%20on%20my%20BWV%20(body%20worn%20video)%20which%20had%20turned%20on.%20The%20conversation%20took%20place%20in%20my%20patrol%20car.%20I%20was%20the%20only%20occupant.%20During%20that%20phone%20call%2C%20Mike%20Olan%20stated%20something%20to%20the%20effect%20that%20it%20was%20unfortunate%20that%20this%20would%20turn%20into%20lawyers%20arguing%20'The%20value%20of%20human%20life.'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMike%20Solan%20asked%20me%20as%20he%20was%20lamenting%20the%20loss%20of%20life%20something%20similar%20to%3A%20'What%20crazy%20argument%20can%20a%20lawyer%20make%20in%20something%20like%20this%3F%20What%20crazy%20thing%20can%20they%20come%20up%20with.'%20I%20responded%20with%20something%20like%3A%20'She's%2026%20years%20old%2C%20what%20value%20is%20there%2C%20who%20cares.'%20I%20intended%20the%20comment%20as%20a%20mockery%20of%20lawyers%20-%20I%20was%20imitating%20what%20a%20lawyer%20tasked%20with%20negotiating%20the%20case%20would%20be%20saying%20and%20being%20sarcastic%20to%20express%20that%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20coming%20up%20with%20crazy%20arguments%20to%20minimize%20the%20payment%2C%26quot%3B%20Auderer%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20laughed%20at%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20how%20these%20incidents%20are%20litigated%20and%20the%20ridiculousness%20of%20how%20I%20have%20watched%20these%20incidents%20play%20out%20as%20two%20parties%20bargain%20over%20a%20tragedy.%20At%20the%20time%20I%20believed%20the%20conversation%20was%20private%20and%20not%20being%20recorded.%20The%20conversation%20was%20also%20not%20within%20the%20course%20of%20my%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20police%20officer%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he%20understands%20that%20without%20context%2C%20the%20comment%20could%20be%20interpreted%20as%20%26quot%3Bhorrifying%20and%20crude%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWithout%20context%2C%20the%20comment%20is%20insensitive%20to%20the%20family%20of%20the%20victim%20when%20in%20reality%20I%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20conversation%20regarding%20the%20callousness%20of%20the%20legal%20system.%20At%20the%20time%20I%20had%20no%20idea%20who%20the%20victim%20was%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAuderer%20said%20he%20does%20understand%20that%20if%20a%20citizen%20were%20to%20hear%20it%20they%20would%20rightfully%20believe%20he%20was%20being%20insensitive%20to%20the%20loss%20of%20a%20human%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20also%20understand%20that%20if%20heard%20it%20could%20diminish%20the%20trust%20in%20the%20Seattle%20Police%20Department%20and%20make%20all%20of%20our%20jobs%20more%20difficult.%20With%20all%20of%20that%20being%20said%20the%20comment%20was%20not%20made%20with%20malice%20or%20a%20hard%20heart%2C%20quite%20the%20opposite.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20intent%20in%20requesting%20rapid%20adjudication%20is%20to%20be%20as%20transparent%20as%20possible.%20I%20am%20willing%20to%20accept%20any%20reasonable%20discipline%20our%20accountability%20partners%20and%20the%20Chief%20of%20Police%20wish%20to%20hand%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20was%20Jaahnavi%20Kandula%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-accident-us-assures-probe-amid-outrage-over-video-of-cop-joking-on-indians-death-4388333%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJaahnavi%20Kandul%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20from%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20pursuing%20a%20master's%20degree%20from%20the%20Northeastern%20University%20campus%20in%20South%20Lake%20Union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20reports%2C%20she%20went%20to%20the%20US%20from%20Bengaluru%20on%20a%20student%20exchange%20programme%20in%202021%20and%20was%20due%20to%20graduate%20in%20December%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Ms%20Kandul's%20death%2C%20her%20university%20decided%20to%20award%20her%20degree%20posthumously%20and%20present%20it%20to%20her%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708571100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Flivp1oog_jaahnavi-kandula_625x300_22_February_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fjaahnavi-kandula-kevin-dave-daniel-auderer-she-was-26-limited-value-what-us-cop-said-after-indian-died-in-accident-5104140%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20police%20officer%20who%20ran%20over%20an%20Indian%20student%20while%20responding%20to%20an%20overdose%20call%2C%20will%20not%20face%20any%20criminal%20charges%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20%26quot%3Bsuffi