6quot%3B%20Hafeez%20revealed%20on%20the%20ARY%20sports%20channel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20shocking%20news%20for%20me%20when%20he%20(team%20trainer)%20told%20me%20that%20he%20was%20told%20to%20not%20check%20the%20players%20fitness%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Hafeez.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20said%20that%20when%20he%20checked%20the%20body%20fat%20percentage%20and%20endurance%20levels%20of%20the%20players%2C%20it%20was%20way%20below%20the%20international%20cricket%20standards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFitness%20in%20modern-day%20cricket%20is%20top%20priority%20for%20all%20teams.%26quot%3B%20Hafeez%20alleged%20that%20when%20tests%20were%20carried%20out%20on%20some%20players%20in%20Australia%2C%20they%20couldn't%20even%20finish%20a%20two-km%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20players'%20skin%20fold%20(body%20fat%20level)%20was%20one-and-a-half%20points%20above%20the%20normal%20limit%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Test%20captain%2C%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Azhar%20Ali%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1468-azhar-ali-playerprofile%5C%22%3EAzhar%20Ali%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20also%20one%20of%20the%20experts%20on%20the%20TV%20show%2C%20recalled%20that%20when%20Pakistan%20had%20gone%20for%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20England%20in%202017%2C%20fitness%20was%20given%20top%20priority%2C%20so%20much%20so%20that%20the%20coaching%20staff%20sent%20a%20player%20(%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Umar%20Akmal%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1043-umar-akmal-playerprofile%5C%22%3EUmar%20Akmal%3C%2Fa%3E)%20back%20because%20he%20had%20failed%20a%20fitness%20test.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArthur%20was%20the%20head%20coach%20of%20the%20team%20that%20won%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20beating%20India%20in%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHafeez%20also%20said%20that%20it%20took%20him%20three%20months%20to%20convince%20Babar%20Azam%20to%20leave%20his%20opening%20slot%20and%