thy%20Wahl%20sued%20ABC%20in%202021%2C%20asserting%20they%20were%20fired%20from%20the%20long-running%20daytime%20%5B%E2%80%A6%5D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Cynthia%20Littleton%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-hospital-abc-covid-vaccination-lawsuit-1235919051%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-hospital-abc-covid-vaccination-lawsuit-1235919051%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fgeneral-hospital-abc-covid-vaccination-lawsuit-1235919051%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Blue%20Aadhaar%20For%20Your%20Child%3A%20What%20It%20Is%2C%20How%20to%20Apply%20And%20More%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAadhaar%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20pivotal%20Know%20Your%20Customer%20(KYC)%20document%20within%20the%20nation%2C%20serving%20as%20a%20crucial%20prerequisite%20for%20accessing%20government%20subsidies%20and%20participating%20in%20various%20welfare%20programs.%20Beyond%20its%20primary%20role%20in%20government%20initiatives%2C%20Aadhaar%20has%20gained%20prominence%20as%20vital%20identity%20proof%20across%20diverse%20sectors.%20This%20is%20attributed%20to%20the%20comprehensive%20information%20it%20encapsulates%2C%20including%20citizens'%20full%20names%2C%20permanent%20addresses%2C%20and%20dates%20of%20birth%2C%20all%20intricately%20linked%20to%20a%20distinctive%2012-digit%20number%20assigned%20by%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAadhaar%20cards%20are%20available%20in%20two%20distinct%20categories%20to%20cater%20to%20different%20demographics.%20The%20first%20category%20is%20tailored%20for%20adults%2C%20encompassing%20the%20standard%20Aadhaar%20card.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20second%20category%20is%20specifically%20designed%20for%20children%20and%20is%20referred%20to%20as%20'Baal%20Aadhaar.'%20This%20specialized%20version%20allows%20parents%20the%20flexibility%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20Aadhaar%20card%20for%20their%20newborns%2C%20ensuring%20a%20seamless%20process%20for%20enrollment%20and%20documentation%20right%20from%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20a%20child's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2Fen%2Fmedia-resources%2Fuidai-documents%2Fparliament-questions%2Flok-sabha%2F4146-baal-aadhaar-card.html%5C%22%3EUIDAI%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20'Baal%20Aadhaar'%2C%20printed%20in%20a%20blue%20coloured%20letter%20for%20communicating%20the%20Aadhaar%20number%20to%20children%20under%20five%20years%20old%2C%20has%20been%20introduced%20by%20UIDAI.%20The%20letter%20informs%20the%20Aadhaar%20holder%20(parents)%20to%20update%20the%20Aadhaar%20details%20with%20biometrics%20on%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years%2C%20failing%20which%20Aadhaar%20will%20be%20deactivated%20and%20will%20not%20be%20valid.%20A%20blue-coloured%20letter%20has%20been%20introduced%20to%20visibly%20distinguish%20the%20letter%20for%20children%2C%20for%20ease%20of%20mass%20communication%20to%20people%20to%20get%20the%20biometrics%20of%20their%20children%20updated%20on%20attaining%20the%20age%20of%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20Section%203(1)%20of%20the%20Aadhaar%20Act%2C%202016%2C%20every%20resident%20is%20entitled%20to%20obtain%20an%20Aadhaar%20number%2C%20including%20children%2C%20by%20submitting%20his%20demographic%20information%20and%20biometric%20information%20during%20the%20process%20of%20enrolment.%20For%20enrolment%20of%20children%20under%205%20years%20old%2C%20biometric%20information%20is%20not%20collected%2C%20only%20demographic%20and%20photograph%20information%20is%20collected.%20The%20Aadhaar%20number%20of%20the%20child%20is%20linked%20with%20either%20of%20the%20parent's%20Aadhaar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENo%20biometric%20data%20on%20the%20child%20is%20required%20for%20'Baal%20Aadhaar'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20children%20under%205%20years%20old%2C%20no%20biometrics%20will%20be%20captured.%20Their%20UID%20will%20be%20processed%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20demographic%20information%20and%20a%20facial%20photograph%20linked%20to%20the%20UID%20of%20their%20parents.%20These%20children%20will%20need%20to%20update%20their%20biometrics%20of%20ten%20fingers%2C%20an%20iris%2C%20and%20a%20facial%20photograph%2C%20when%20they%20turn%205%20and%2015.%20Intimation%20to%20this%20effect%20will%20be%20mentioned%20in%20the%20original%20Aadhaar%20letter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20easily%20book%20an%20appointment%20for%20your%20child's%20Aadhaar%20card%20online%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Head%20to%20the%20official%20website%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20the%20Unique%20Identification%20Authority%20of%20India%20(UIDAI)%20website%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Navigate%20to%20%26quot%3BMy%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFind%20the%20%26quot%3BMy%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%20section%20and%20click%20on%20%26quot%3BBook%20an%20Appointment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Choose%20%26quot%3BChild%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESelect%20%26quot%3BNew%20Aadhaar%26quot%3B%20and%20enter%20your%20mobile%20number%20and%20the%20security%20code%20(captcha).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%26quot%3BRelationship%20with%20Head%20of%20Family%2C%26quot%3B%20choose%20%26quot%3BChild%20(0-5%20years).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Fill%20in%20Your%20Child's%20Details%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarefully%20enter%20your%20child's%20information%2C%20including%20name%2C%20date%20of%20birth%2C%20and%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEnsure%20you%20have%20the%20required%20documents%3A%20your%20child's%20birth%20certificate%20and%20your%20own%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Book%20Your%20Appointment%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoose%20a%20convenient%20date%20and%20time%20at%20a%20nearby%20Aadhaar%20Seva%20Kendra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConfirm%20your%20booking%2C%20and%20you're%20all%20set.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere's%20how%20to%20get%20your%20child's%20Aadhaar%20card%20(Blue%20Aadhaar)%20offline%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Find%20an%20Enrollment%20Center%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisit%20any%20Aadhaar%20Seva%20Kendra%20or%20Permanent%20Enrollment%20Center.%20You%20can%20locate%20one%20near%20you%20on%20the%20UIDAI%20website%3A%20https%3A%2F%2Fuidai.gov.in%2F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2.%20Inform%20the%20officials%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETell%20them%20you%20want%20to%20enroll%20your%20child%20for%20a%20Blue%20Aadhaar%20card.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E3.%20Fill%20out%20the%20form%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECarefully%20complete%20the%20Aadhaar%20enrollment%20form%20with%20your%20child's%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%20Gather%20the%20documents%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMake%20sure%20you%20have%20the%20following%20documents%20readily%20available%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnYour%20Aadhaar%20card%3A%20As%20proof%20of%20parentage.%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20child's%20birth%20certificate%3A%20As%20proof%20of%20birth%20and%20identity.%3Cbr%3E%5CnYour%20address%20proof%3A%20Ration%20card%2C%20electricity%20bill%2C%20etc.%3Cbr%3E%5CnTwo%20passport-sized%20photos%20of%20your%20child%3A%20Optional%2C%20but%20helpful%20if%20the%20center's%20photo%20service%20is%20unavailable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E5.%20Submit%20Your%20Application%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHand%20over%20the%20completed%20form%20and%20all%20the%20required%20documents%20to%20the%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708568040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-11%2Ftqhviek_aadhaar-card-650_625x300_11_November_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbaal-aadhaar-card-blue-aadhaar-for-your-child-what-it-is-how-to-apply-and-more-5103976%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Parents%20have%20the%20option%20to%20apply%20for%20the%20Baal%20Aadhaar%20Card%2C%