20the%20UK%20for%20the%20next%20seven%20years%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20was%20the%20sole%20director%20of%20the%20restaurant%2C%20trading%20under%20the%20company%20name%20of%20Tender%20Love%20Ltd%20since%20June%202014.%20In%20the%20UK%2C%20restaurants%20serving%20cuisine%20associated%20with%20countries%20in%20the%20Indian%20subcontinent%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20Nepal%2C%20are%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20Indian%20restaurants.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImmigration%20Enforcement%20officers%20carried%20out%20an%20operation%20at%20the%20premises%20of%20Taste%20of%20Raj%20Indian%20restaurant%20in%20Hertfordshire%20in%20March%202020%2C%20finding%20three%20men%20with%20no%20right%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK.%20The%20three%20workers%2C%20originally%20from%20Bangladesh%20and%20aged%20in%20their%2040s%2C%20told%20investigators%20they%20had%20worked%20at%20the%20restaurant%20for%20between%20four%20days%20and%20up%20to%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHussain%20had%20employed%20them%20without%20conducting%20right-to-work%20checks%20and%20also%20failed%20to%20keep%20the%20required%20documentation%20proving%20they%20were%20eligible%20to%20work%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20the%20officers%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIllegal%20working%20cheats%20honest%20workers%20out%20of%20employment%2C%20puts%20vulnerable%20people%20at%20risk%2C%20and%20defrauds%20the%20public%20purse.%20We're%20clamping%20down%20on%20illegal%20working%20by%20ramping%20up%20enforcement%20activity%20and%20tripling%20fines%20for%20rogue%20employers.%20We%20will%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20partners%20including%20the%20Insolvency%20Service%20to%20tackle%20illegal%20migration%20in%20all%20its%20forms%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suran%20Padiachie%2C%20Home%20Office%20Immigration%20Enforcement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Secretary%20of%20State%20for%20Business%20and%20Trade%2C%20Kemi%20Badenoch%2C%20accepted%20a%20disqualification%20undertaking%20from%20Hussain%20which%20means%20his%20seven-year%20ban%20began%20last%20week.%20It%20imposes%20several%20restrictions%20on%20his%20business%20activities%20and%20prevents%20him%20from%20becoming%20involved%20in%20the%20promotion%2C%20formation%20or%20management%20of%20a%20company%20without%20the%20permission%20of%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708567260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Femid3i28_taste-of-raj-stanstead-abbotts-facebook_625x300_22_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmanager-of-indian-restaurant-in-uk-banned-for-hiring-illegal-workers-5099711%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20manager%20of%20an%20Indian%20restaurant%20and%20takeaway%20in%20eastern%20England%20has%20been%20handed%20a%20seven-year%20ban%20as%20a%20company%20director%20after%20employing%20three%20illegal%20workers%20from%20Bangladesh.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmanager-of-indian-restaurant-in-uk-banned-for-hiring-illegal-workers-5099711%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmanager-of-indian-restaurant-in-uk-banned-for-hiring-illegal-workers-5099711%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fmanager-of-indian-restaurant-in-uk-banned-for-hiring-illegal-workers-5099711%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Moment%20giant%20Antarctica%20drone%20takes%20off%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708566030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FF78A%2Fproduction%2F_132707336_p0hd91zf.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fscience-environment-68363623%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Scientists%20want%20to%20use%