esday%20the%20crucial%20support%20provided%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20including%20equipment%20suitable%20for%20high-altitude%20conflict%2C%20which%20proved%20invaluable%20to%20the%20Indian%20army%20during%20the%20tense%20early%20months%20of%20the%20standoff.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20continue%20to%20discuss%20the%20challenges%20we%20face%20with%20our%20northern%20neighbour.%20The%20possibility%20that%20we%20may%20encounter%20a%20similar%20situation.%20What%20we%20faced%20in%202020%20is%20keeping%20us%20active%20all%20the%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20at%20an%20event%20organised%20to%20encourage%20collaboration%20between%20the%20Indian%20and%20US%20defence%20industries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAramane%20continued%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20one%20thing%20which%20helped%20us%20very%20quickly%20in%20the%20entire%20episode%20was%20the%20intelligence%2C%20the%20situation%20awareness%2C%20which%20the%20US%20equipment%20and%20US%20government%20could%20help%20us%20with.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20asserted%20that%20it%20was%20essential%20that%20India%20felt%20assured%20of%20the%20United%20States%E2%80%99%20support%20against%20a%20shared%20%E2%80%9Cthreat%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20strong%20resolve%20that%20we%20support%20each%20other%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20common%20threat%20is%20going%20to%20be%20of%20critical%20importance%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20perhaps%20the%20most%20explicit%20articulation%20by%20a%20senior%20Indian%20government%20official%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20defence%20cooperation%20with%20the%20United%20States%20is%20geared%20towards%20fending%20off%20China.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20giving%20a%20faceoff%20to%20our%20neighbour%20in%20almost%20all%20the%20fronts%20that%20we%20have%20with%20them.%20Wherever%20there%20is%20a%20mountain%20pass%2C%20we%20are%20stationed%20there%20to%20face%20the%20eventuality%20and%20wherever%20there%20is%20a%20road%2C%20we%20have%20to%20be%20ready%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20defence%20secretary%20asserted%20that%20as%20India%20confronts%20China%2C%20New%20Delhi%20expects%20Washington%20to%20stand%20alongside%20them.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%A6we%20are%20standing%20against%20a%20bully%20in%20a%20very%20determined%20fashion%20and%20we%20expect%20that%20our%20friend%20%5Bthe%5D%20US%20will%20be%20there%20with%20us%20in%20case%20we%20need%20their%20support%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20further%20expressed%20gratitude%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Csupport%20and%20the%20resolve%20from%20our%20friends%20in%20supporting%20us%20during%20such%20an%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fdefence%2Findia-acquires-11000-extreme-cold-gear-sets-from-us-army%2Farticleshow%2F78922920.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20had%20been%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20India%2C%20under%20the%20Logistics%20Exchange%20Memorandum%20of%20Agreement%20signed%20with%20the%20US%2C%20had%20urgently%20acquired%20the%20Extended%20Cold%20Weather%20Clothing%20System%2C%20as%20New%20Delhi%20deployed%20thousands%20of%20troops%20to%20the%20Himalayan%20heights%20following%20the%20onset%20of%20the%20latest%20standoff%20with%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdditionally%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2021-10-28%2Findia-deploys-u-s-weapons-to-fortify-disputed-border-with-china%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20deployed%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20US-made%20Chinook%20helicopters%2C%20ultra-light%20towed%20howitzers%20and%20rifles%20for%20troops%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20as%20per%20reports.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAramane