20in%20Ceylon%2C%20the%20radio%20station%20started%20beaming%20out%20of%20programmes%20to%20India%20and%20the%20neighbourhood.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGenerations%20of%20Indians%20grew%20up%20listening%20to%20his%20voice%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EBinaca%20Geetmala%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%E2%80%93%20named%20after%20a%20toothpaste%20brand%20%E2%80%93%20every%20Wednesday%20at%208%20pm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20it%2C%20Sayani%20listed%2016%20songs%20in%20the%20order%20of%20popularity%2C%20the%20final%20one%20being%20introduced%20with%20a%20bugle%2C%20or%20in%20his%20words%2C%20with%20a%20Bigul.%20His%20sweet%20voice%20and%20warm%2C%20friendly%20tone%20endeared%20him%20to%20millions%20and%20his%20pet%20phrases%20%E2%80%93%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ebehnon%20aur%20bhaiyon%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(sisters%20and%20brothers)%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eaur%20ab%20agli%20badaan%20par%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(on%20the%20next%20step)%2C%20became%20wildly%20popular%2C%20or%20went%20viral%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20language.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20list%20was%20prepared%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20postcards%20received%20from%20listeners%20%E2%80%93%20there%20were%20often%20reports%20of%20mass%20postcards%20being%20sent%20by%20producers%20themselves%2C%20which%20Sayani%20had%20to%20discard.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20responses%20came%20from%20every%20part%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20he%20often%20picked%20out%20the%20odd%20postcard%20and%20read%20them%20out%2C%20and%20listeners%20became%20very%20familiar%20with%20names%20they%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20before%2C%20such%20as%20Jhumri%20Talaiya%20and%20Rajnandgaon%2C%20which%20are%20now%20memes.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESayani%20came%20into%20commercial%20broadcasting%20thanks%20to%20his%20elder%20brother%20Hamid%2C%20who%20used%20to%20run%20a%20show%20called