%20that%20climatically%20fresh%20yellow%20dates%20would%20be%20new%20in%20India%20but%20would%20also%20grow%20very%20well.%20Dried%20dates%20are%20quite%20common%20but%20fresh%20dates%20are%20relatively%20unknown%20but%20extremely%20nutritious%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20Nagendra%20was%20not%20sure%20how%20this%20variety%20of%20dates%20would%20grow%20in%20the%20climatic%20conditions%2C%20he%20started%20with%20just%2020%20acres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20grown%20up%20seeing%20wild%20dates%20growing%20in%20the%20region%20but%20not%20yellow%20dates.%20While%20it%20could%20have%20been%20a%20huge%20miss%2C%20thankfully%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%2C%20and%20the%20climate%20suits%20perfectly%20to%20grow%20the%20plant%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20had%20to%20import%20the%20Yellow%20Dates%20seeds%20from%20abroad%20as%20these%20are%20not%20available%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20However%2C%20one%20bite%20of%20the%20fruit%20was%20all%20it%20took%20to%20realise%20its%20immense%20consumer%20appeal%20and%20market%20potential%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20taste%20was%20addicting%20and%20I%20knew%20once%20the%20consumers%20find%20out%20about%20the%20fruit%2C%20it%20is%20going%20to%20be%20a%20success.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20my%20friends%20from%20college%20and%20we%20raised%20some%20funds.%20In%202021%2C%20I%20had%20a%20great%20yield%20and%20we%20were%20selling%20in%20and%20around%20Anantpur%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fkavi-6-1708522576.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nagendra%20now%20sells%20Yellow%20Dates%20on%20platforms%20such%20as%20Big%20Basket%2C%20Zepto%20etc.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads