%20not%20just%20a%20cosmetic%20device.%20A%20cancer%20patient%20already%20deals%20with%20a%20plethora%20of%20problems.%20Being%20able%20to%20remove%20one%20burden%20and%20add%20certain%20value%20to%20a%20cancer%20patient%E2%80%99s%20life%20gives%20me%20a%20huge%20sense%20of%20contentment.%20My%20role%20is%20small%20but%20the%20satisfaction%20that%20I%20get%20out%20of%20it%20is%20immense%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat.%20All%20photos%3A%20Raghuveer%20Surupa)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708524524000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FEva-Scalp-Cooling-1-1708521986.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D342777%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mumbai-based%20Raghuveer%20Surupa%2C%20founder%20of%20Stemtech%20Medical%20Devices%2C%20created%20the%20Eva%20Scalp%20Cooling%20System%20to%20help%20patients%20experiencing%20hair%20loss%20during%20chemotherapy.%20The%20system%2C%20designed%20to%20protect%20hair%20follicles%2C%20was%20showcased%20on%20Shark%20Tank%20India%20and%20received%20a%20Rs%2030%20lakh%20investment.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F342777%2Fprevent-hair-loss-chemotherapy-cancer-care-raghuveer-surupa-eva-scalp-cooling-system-shark-tank%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Contrary%20to%20Claims%2C%20RTIs%20Reveal%20Union%20Govt%20Doesn't%20Have%20States%E2%80%99%20Reports%20on%20Forest%20Tags%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17202229%2FForest-in-Odisha.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20As%20per%20a%201996%20judgment%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20states%20were%20to%20form%20expert%20committees%20to%20identify%20forests%20that%20satisfy%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20the%20term%20even%20if%20those%20tracts%20were%20not%20officially%20recorded%20as%20forests%20(for%20instance%2C%20deemed%20forests%20such%20as%20the%20Aravalli%20hill%20range%20in%20Haryana%2C%20are%20not%20officially%20recognised%20as%20forests).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%202011%20judgment%2C%20also%20by%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20stressed%20that%20the%201996%20judgment%20be%20followed%20and%20states%20prepare%20%E2%80%9Cgeo-referenced%20district%20forest-maps%E2%80%9D%20to%20document%20all%20forests%20under%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20of%201980.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBoth%20these%20judgments%20have%20not%20been%20followed%3A%20the%20Union%20government%20has%20no%20record%20of%20reports%20by%20state%20expert%20committees%2C%20and%20no%20documentation%20of%20geo-referenced%20forest%20plots%2C%20according%20to%20RTI%20responses%20received%20by%20a%20conservationist%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-has-no-details-of-panel-report-on-deemed-forests-rti-101708456003179.html%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereported%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20February%2021.%20This%20is%20also%20contrary%20to%20the%20environment%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20claims%20%E2%80%93%20that%20deemed%20forests%20identified%20by%20states%20have%20been%20recorded%20%E2%80%93%20in%20its%20response%20to%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Amendment%20Bill%202023%20submitted%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20in%20July%20last%20year%2C%20per%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-has-no-details-of-panel-report-on-deemed-forests-rti-101708456003179.html%23%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enews%20report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ETwo%20judgments%20to%20identify%2C%20document%20unrecognised%20forests%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20of%201980%20provides%20for%20the%20conservation%20of%20forests%20in%20the%20country%20in%20several%20ways%2C%20including%20restricting%20diversion%20of%20forest%20land%20for%20projects%20unless%20cleared%20by%20a%20Forest%20Advisory%20Committee.%20In%20March%202023%2C%20however%2C%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry%20sought%20to%20amend%20this%20Act.%20The%20amendment%20made%20several%20changes%2C%20including%20in%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Act%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20now%20called%20the%20Van%20(Sanrakshan%20Evam%20Samvardhan)%20Adhiniyam%202023.%20However%2C%20experts%20across%20various%20fields%20raised%20numerous%20concerns%20about%20the%20Amendment%2C%20including%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20would%20narrow%20the%20definition%20of%20forests%20as%20laid%20down%20by%20a%20landmark%20judgment%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%201996%2C%20and%20thereby%20exempt%20a%20lot%20of%20forest%20land%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20deemed%20forests%20and%20community%20forests%20%E2%80%93%20from%20legal%20protection.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20the%201996%20judgment%20(also%20called%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fsearch%2F%3FformInput%3Dgodavarman%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EGodavarman%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20order)%2C%20lands%20that%20satisfy%20the%20dictionary%20meaning%20of%20a%20forest%20should%20also%20be%20recognised%20as%20forests%2C%20and%20be%20brought%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20of%201980.%20The%20court%20ordered%20that%20states%20should%20form%20State%20Expert%20Committees%20or%20SECs%20to%20put%20together%20state-wise%20reports%20on%20all%20such%20lands%20identified%20as%20forests.%20This%20report%20was%20to%20then%20be%20shared%20with%20the%20Union%20environment%20ministry.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiaenvironmentportal.org.in%2Ffiles%2FLafarge.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E2011%20judgment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(called%20the%20%3Cem%3ELafarge%20%3C%2Fem%3Eorder)%2C%20also%20by%20the%20apex%20court%2C%20stressed%20that%20the%201996%20judgment%20be%20followed%20and%20states%20also%20prepare%20%E2%80%9Cgeo-referenced%20district%20forest-maps%E2%80%9D%20containing%20the%20details%20of%20the%20location%20and%20boundary%20of%20each%20plot%20of%20land%20that%20may%20be%20defined%20as%20%E2%80%9Cforest%E2%80%9D%20(such%20as%20deemed%20forests%2C%20which%20are%20officially%20not%20recognised%20as%20forests%2C%20but%20would%20be%20if%20both%20these%20orders%20were%20followed).%20It%20also%20specified%20that%20a%20Geographic%20Information%20System%20(GIS)-based%20decision%20support%20database%20containing%20these%20district-wise%20details%20of%20each%20plot%20of%20land%20be%20created%20and%20regularly%20updated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20the%20environment%20ministry%20does%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20reports%20prepared%20by%20SECs%20which%20identified%20deemed%20forests%20in%20every%20state%20as%20per%20the%201996%20order%2C%20according%20to%20information%20received%20under%20a%20Right%20to%20Information%20(RTI)%20application.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E%E2%80%98False%20assurances%E2%80%99%20by%20the%20environment%20ministry%3F%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%20gave%20this%20information%20to%20Prakriti%20Srivastava%2C%20former%20Indian%20Forest%20Service%20officer%20(former%20Principal%20Chief%20Conservator%20of%20Forests%2C%20Kerala)%20and%20a%20co-petitioner%20of%20one%20of%20the%20many%20petitions%20heard%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20against%20the%20amendment%20to%20the%20old%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%2C%20in%20a%20series%20of%20responses%20to%20her%20queries%20under%20the%20RTI%20Act.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20environment%20ministry%20told%20Srivastava%20on%20January%2025%20this%20year%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Crequisite%20information%20is%20not%20available%20in%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20division%20of%20the%20Ministry%E2%80%9D.%20It%20transferred%20her%20query%20to%20the%20PCCFs%20of%20all%20states%20to%20provide%20her%20with%20replies%2C%20reported%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fcentre-has-no-details-of-panel-report-on-deemed-forests-rti-101708456003179.html%23%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20January%2020%20this%20year%2C%20Srivastava%20had%20also%20sought%20details%20of%20all%20geo-referenced%20district%20forest%20maps%20with%20the%20Ministry%20as%20per%20the%202011%20Lafarge%20order%2C%20the%20latest%20GIS%20maps%20for%20all%20States%20and%20Union%20Territories%20containing%20the%20location%20details%20of%20the%20plots%20of%20land%20that%20may%20be%20defined%20as%20a%20forest%2C%20and%20whether%20a%20GIS-based%20decision%20support%20database%20was%20created%20as%20directed%20by%20the%20SC%2C%20and%20if%20so%2C%20a%20link%20to%20that.%20However%2C%20the%20weblink%20the%20ministry%20gave%20did%20not%20provide%20geo-referenced%20maps%20of%20these%20forests%2C%20Srivastava%20told%20Hindustan%20Times.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%2C%20per%20the%20news%20report%2C%20is%20contrary%20to%20what%20the%20ministry%20said%20in%20its%20report%20to%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20on%20the%20Forest%20Conservation%20Amendment%20bill%202023%20submitted%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20last%20year%2C%20as%20part%20of%20the%20steps%20that%20are%20required%20to%20make%20an%20amendment%20a%20law.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPer%20the%20news%20report%2C%20the%20ministry%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdeemed%20forests%20as%20identified%20by%20expert%20committees%20of%20the%20states%2C%20have%20been%20taken%20on%20record%20and%20hence%20the%20provision%20of%20the%20Act%20will%20be%20applicable%20in%20such%20lands%20also%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20giving%20the%20impression%20to%20several%20environmental%20groups%20that%20the%20data%20was%20already%20available%20with%20the%20union%20environment%20ministry%2C%20per%20the%20HT%20report.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20%E2%80%9Cshocking%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Chorrifying%E2%80%9D%20that%20the%20ministry%20has%20made%20such%20%E2%80%9Cfalse%20assurances%E2%80%9D%2C%20Srivastava%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHT%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2019%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20passed%20an%20interim%20order%20after%20hearing%20several%20petitions%20by%20groups%20and%20organisations%20against%20the%20changes%20to%20the%20old%20Forest%20Conservation%20Act%20that%20effectively%20dilute%20its%20power%20to%20conserve%20forests.%20Apart%20from%20instructing%20states%20and%20UTs%20to%20uphold%20the%20definition%20of%20forests%20as%20per%20its%20dictionary%20meaning%20in%20identifying%20lands%20that%20are%20forested%20but%20not%20recognised%20legally%20as%20forests%2C%20the%20SC%20in%20its%20interim%20order%20also%20directed%20that%20the%20SEC%20reports%20by%20submitted%20to%20the%20Ministry%20by%20March%2031%20this%20year%2C%20and%20that%20the%20environment%20ministry%20maintain%20these%20records%2C%20digitise%20it%20and%20make%20it%20available%20on%20its%20official%20website%20by%20April%2015%2C%202024.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708524030000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F17202229%2FForest-in-Odisha.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fforest-rti-union-government-states%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20environment%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20RTI%20responses%20suggest%20that%20it%20gave%20'false%20assurances'%20about%20having%20recorded%20states%E2%80%99%20reports%20to%20the%20Joint%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20that%20scrutinised%20the%20Amendment%20to%20the%20Forest%20Act.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fforest-rti-union-government-states%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98The%20Holdovers%E2%80%99%3A%20A%20Coming-of-Age%20Tale%20Triggering%20a%20Midlife%20Awakening%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21183836%2F2.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Hunham%20(Paul%20Giamatti)%20sets%20high%20standards%20for%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeaching%20ancient%20civilisation%20at%20a%20prestigious%20boys%E2%80%99%20school%20in%20New%20England%2C%20he%20also%20inflicts%20his%20tyrannical%20expectations%20on%20his%20students.%20One%20can%20see%20why%20he%E2%80%99s%20hated%3B%20in%20an%20ocean%20of%20Cs%2C%20Ds%20and%20Fs%2C%20the%20highest%20grade%20he%20awards%20is%20a%20B%2B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20antagonises%20his%20headmaster%20(a%20former%20student%20of%20his)%20when%20he%20refuses%20to%20pass%20a%20senator%E2%80%99s%20son%2C%20resulting%20in%20him%20losing%20his%20seat%20in%20Princeton.%20He%20often%20invokes%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20honour%20code%3A%20%E2%80%9CBarton%20men%20don%E2%80%99t%20lie%E2%80%9D%2C%20especially%20around%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20something%20more%20appears%20to%20be%20going%20on%20with%20Hunham.%20As%20much%20as%20he%20plays%20the%20part%20of%20a%20cranky%20faculty%20member%20who%20barely%20ever%20leaves%20the%20school%20premises%2C%20his%20eyes%20soften%20as%20he%20approaches%20the%20manager%20of%20the%20school%E2%80%99s%20cafeteria%2C%20Mary%20(Da%E2%80%99Vine%20Joy%20Randolph)%2C%20who%20lost%20her%20son%20Curtis%20in%20Vietnam%20only%20weeks%20ago.%20He%20asks%20how%20she%E2%80%99s%20doing%2C%20not%20with%20pity%2C%20but%20genuine%20empathy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHunham%20%E2%80%93%20sporting%20a%20lazy%20left%20eye%2C%20a%20liking%20for%20stiff%20bourbon%20and%20a%20condition%20that%20causes%20him%20to%20reek%20of%20body%20odour%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20%E2%80%93%20is%20hiding%20behind%20a%20facade.%20As%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20even%20though%20people%20around%20him%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20care%20much%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20more%20to%20Paul%20Hunham.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlexander%20Payne%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Holdovers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20brilliant%20portrait%20of%20a%20man%E2%80%99s%20dissatisfaction%20with%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20earlier%20films%2C%20Payne%20has%20fixated%20on%20showing%20fairly%20intelligent%20men%20at%20their%20most%20fallible.%20Like%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Descendants%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2009)%2C%20the%20way%20George%20Clooney%E2%80%99s%20character%20runs%20from%20his%20house%20after%20learning%20about%20how%20his%20comatose%20wife%20was%20having%20an%20affair.%20Or%20Giamatti%E2%80%99s%20late-30s%20character%20in%20%3Cem%3ESideways%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2004)%20stealing%20cash%20from%20his%20mother%20because%20he%E2%80%99s%20too%20embarrassed%20to%20admit%20to%20his%20less-than-ideal%20financial%20condition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Holdovers%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Giamatti%E2%80%99s%20character%20might%20act%20confident%20and%20acerbic%20but%20behind%20the%20facade%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20a%20man%20deeply%20ashamed%20of%20never%20making%20good%20on%20his%20own%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FAhKLpJmHhIg%3Fsi%3D7b9HjDpl1XsBv9pO%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPayne%2C%20known%20for%20unearthing%20the%20extraordinary%20within%20the%20mundane%2C%20frames%20two%20unlikely%20companions%20for%20Hunham%20during%20Christmas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAngus%20Tully%20(Dominic%20Sessa)%2C%20a%20student%20of%20Hunham%E2%80%99s%2C%20isn%E2%80%99t%20someone%20to%20mince%20his%20words.%20He%E2%80%99s%20respectful%20and%20curt%20towards%20his%20teacher.%20He%E2%80%99s%20the%20first%20one%20to%20tell%20him%20that%20he%20%E2%80%9Csmells%20like%20fish%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft%20behind%20in%20school%20during%20the%20holidays%20by%20a%20mother%20who%20is%20still%20adjusting%20to%20a%20new%20marital%20life%2C%20Angus%20is%20not%20your%20typical%20rebellious%20teenager.%20He%E2%80%99s%20forthright%20with%20his%20thoughts%20and%20opinions%2C%20veers%20a%20bit%20on%20the%20naughty%20side%2C%20an%20effortless%20liar%2C%20but%20also%20kind%20and%20vulnerable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESessa%2C%20who%20is%20making%20his%20acting%20debut%20opposite%20Giamatti%2C%20is%20sensational%20as%20someone%20who%20never%20lets%20his%20character%E2%80%99s%20inexperience%20become%20a%20crutch%20for%20his%20childish%20behaviour.%20Payne%E2%80%99s%20masterstroke%20is%20how%20equal%20Hunham%20and%20Tully%E2%80%99s%20dynamic%20feels.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMary%2C%20as%20a%20grieving%20mother%2C%20completes%20this%20trio%20of%20sad%2C%20abandoned%20residents%20of%20the%20boarding%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERandolph%20is%20excellent%20and%20understated%20as%20Mary%2C%20never%20milking%20the%20tragedy%20to%20get%20any%20character%20in%20the%20film%20or%20the%20audience%20to%20feel%20sorry%20for%20her.%20She%E2%80%99s%20tussling%20with%20her%20hurt%20by%20dousing%20it%20in%20alcohol%20and%20late-night%20TV.%20She%20becomes%20the%20conduit%20between%20Paul%20and%20Angus%2C%20who%20seem%20to%20be%20constantly%20at%20odds%2C%20never%20able%20to%20find%20middle%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWritten%20by%20David%20Hemingson%2C%20Payne%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20assured%20and%20restrained%20in%20all%20the%20right%20ways.%20It%20might%20seem%20like%20it%20belongs%20to%20the%20sub-genre%20of%20%E2%80%98comfort%E2%80%99%20watches%20during%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20plenty%20of%20darkness%20under%20the%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20throwaway%20moments%20in%20a%20scene%20tells%20us%20how%20Mary%E2%80%99s%20son%20Curtis%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20go%20to%20college%2C%20like%20most%20of%20his%20classmates%20from%20Barton.%20However%2C%20she%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20enough%20money%20despite%20the%20partial%20scholarship.%20Not%20being%20able%20to%20go%20to%20college%20meant%20that%20he%20got%20drafted%20to%20Vietnam%2C%20unlike%20his%20privileged%20white%20peers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20brief%20moment%20between%20Tully%20and%20Hunham%20tells%20us%20how%20they%E2%80%99re%20both%20grappling%20with%20mental%20health%20issues.%20Payne%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20overemphasise%20his%20intent%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20all%20the%20more%20impactful.%20A%20father-son%20reunion%20is%20unexpectedly%20cut%20short%2C%20mirroring%20how%20life%20never%20quite%20makes%20space%20for%20picture-perfect%20farewells.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20weighty%20themes%2C%20Payne%E2%80%99s%20knack%20to%20find%20humour%20in%20life%E2%80%99s%20awkward%20happenstances%20remains%20top-class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20film%20that%20tries%20to%20be%20specific%20with%20its%20period%20detailing%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20manner%20that%20it%20employs%20its%20music%20or%20even%20the%20dissolves.%20But%20it%20rarely%20gives%20in%20to%20the%20temptation%20of%20being%20overtly%20nostalgic%20about%20the%20%E2%80%98good%20ol%E2%80%99%20days%E2%80%99%20or%20leaning%20on%20sentimentality%20to%20drive%20its%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Holdovers%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20splendid%20ode%20to%20how%20one%20can%20overcome%20generational%20friction%20once%20they%20get%20to%20know%20another%20person%20and%20how%20it%20sometimes%20lays%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20life-changing%20friendship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Payne%2C%20the%20generation%20gap%20is%20a%20myth%20because%20human%20experience%20rarely%20changes.%20%E2%80%9CEverything%20from%20the%20disgusting%20to%20the%20sublime%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20as%20Hunham%20tells%20Tully%20in%20one%20scene.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20lucid%20explanation%20for%20how%20some%20coming-of-age%20tales%20can%20trigger%20midlife%20awakenings.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708522212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21183836%2F2.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-holdovers-coming-of-age-tale-midlife-awakening%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Written%20by%20David%20Hemingson%2C%20Alexander%20Payne%E2%80%99s%20film%20is%20assured%20and%20restrained%20in%20all%20the%20right%20ways.%20It%20might%20seem%20like%20it%20belongs%20to%20the%20sub-genre%20of%20%E2%80%98comfort%E2%80%99%20watches%20during%20the%20holiday%20season%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20plenty%20of%20darkness%20under%20the%20edges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fthe-holdovers-coming-of-age-tale-midlife-awakening%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fali%20Nariman%2C%20The%20Conscience%20Keeper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21181850%2FUntitled-design-3-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20phrase%20that%20best%20described%20Fali%20Nariman%20was%20conscience%20keeper%2C%20and%20that%20is%20how%20I%20will%20always%20remember%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFali%20Sam%20Nariman%2C%20who%20was%20happy%20to%20be%20addressed%20as%20%E2%80%98Fali%E2%80%99%20by%20young%20and%20old%20alike%2C%20was%20conscience-keeper%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India%2C%20to%20the%20bar%20and%20the%20bench%20alike%2C%20to%20the%20various%20state%20governments%20he%20had%20represented%20over%20the%20decades%2C%20and%20even%20to%20the%20nation.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20just%2046%20when%2C%20having%20represented%20the%20Union%20government%20as%20Additional%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20from%201972%20to%201975%2C%20he%20was%20faced%20with%20the%20imposition%20of%20the%20Emergency%20on%20June%2025%2C%201975.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFali%20refused%20to%20stand%20by%20and%20defend%20this%20suspension%20of%20constitutional%20rights.%20He%20promptly%20resigned.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3EAt%20a%20time%20when%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20judges%20had%20folded%20up%20like%20a%20defeated%20pack%20of%20cards%2C%20this%20doughty%20young%20lawyer%20stood%20up%20and%20was%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20another%20time%2C%20much%20later%2C%20Fali%20returned%20the%20brief%20of%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20in%20the%20prestigious%20Narmada%20Dam%20rehabilitation%20case%2C%20when%20he%20learnt%20that%20the%20same%20government%20was%20looking%20the%20other%20way%20as%20Christian%20tribals%20were%20being%20attacked%20in%20the%20Dang%20district%2C%20their%20churches%20burnt%2C%20and%20their%20bibles%20desecrated.%20Fali%20first%20tried%20to%20prevail%20upon%20the%20minister%20who%20briefed%20him%20to%20ensure%20government%20intervention%20and%20protection%20of%20the%20hapless%20minority.%20But%20when%20he%20found%20that%20Christian%20tribals%20were%20being%20attacked%20and%20killed%20despite%20assurances%20by%20the%20minister%2C%20he%20refused%20to%20appear%20for%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20equally%20questioning%20of%20himself%20and%20the%20role%20he%20unwittingly%20played%20in%20certain%20cases.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffali-nariman-obituary-indira-jaising%5C%22%3EAt%20a%20Time%20When%20the%20Battles%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20Future%20Will%20Be%20Fought%20in%20its%20Courts%2C%20We%20Will%20Miss%20Fali%20Nariman%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20successfully%20defended%20the%20Union%20Carbide%20Corporation%20and%20its%20American%20directors%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20Bhopal%20gas%20disaster%2C%20and%20having%20brought%20a%20modicum%20of%20closure%20to%20the%20legal%20battles%20through%20the%20%24470%20million%20settlement%20that%20he%20helped%20negotiate%20before%20getting%20the%20imprimatur%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20Fali%20was%20later%20anguished%20by%20the%20enormous%20human%20tragedy%20that%20Carbide%20had%20inflicted.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20arrived%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20in%202010%2C%20he%20asked%20me%20to%20represent%20his%20close%20friend%2C%20the%20former%20managing%20director%20of%20UCC%20India%2C%20in%20a%20curative%20petition%20initiated%20by%20the%20then%20Attorney%20General%20for%20India.%20And%20when%20I%20asked%20him%20whether%20he%20would%20lead%20me%20in%20the%20matter%2C%20his%20answer%20was%20a%20deeply%20disturbed%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20can%E2%80%99t%2C%20I%20can%E2%80%99t%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20tortured%20by%20it%E2%80%9D.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20couple%20of%20years%20later%20Fali%20devoted%20a%20lengthy%20chapter%20to%20this%20anguish%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fadm-jabalpur-emergency-niren-de-tushar-mehta%5C%22%3Ehis%20memoir%2C%20%3Cem%3EBefore%20Memory%20Fades%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELess%20disturbed%20but%20nonetheless%20keenly%20aware%20that%20perhaps%20he%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20about%20a%20less-than-perfect%20system%20for%20the%20selection%20of%20judges%2C%20Fali%20always%20wondered%20how%20things%20might%20have%20turned%20out%20if%20he%20had%20not%20been%20as%20successful%20in%20arguing%20the%20first%20and%20second%20Judges%20cases%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F1294854%2F%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3ES.P.%20Gupta%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F753224%2F%5C%22%3E%20%3Ci%3ESupreme%20Court%20Advocates%20on%20Record%20Association%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Those%20cases%20led%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcollegium-system-judges-knockout-blow%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98collegium%E2%80%99%20system%20of%20judicial%20appointments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20giving%20India%20the%20unique%20distinction%20of%20being%20the%20only%20major%20nation%20where%20judges%20select%20future%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20later%20years%2C%20Fali%20continued%20as%20conscience%20keeper%20through%20his%20calmly%20reasoned%2C%20gentle%2C%20yet%20persuasive%20reminders%20of%20the%20strengths%20and%20weaknesses%20of%20our%20judicial%20system.%20Putting%20pen%20to%20paper%20time%20and%20again%20during%20the%20past%2010%20years%2C%20he%20wrote%20%3Cem%3EThe%20State%20of%20the%20Nation%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2013)%2C%20%3Cem%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20Legal%20System%20%E2%80%93%20Can%20it%20be%20Saved%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2017)%2C%20%3Cem%3EGod%20Save%20the%20Hon%E2%80%99ble%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2018)%2C%20%3Cem%3EHarmony%20Amidst%20Disharmony%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2022)%2C%20and%20even%20the%20very%20recent%20guide%20for%20citizens%2C%20%3Cem%3EYou%20Must%20Know%20Your%20Constitution%3C%2Fem%3E%20(2023).%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20of%20course%2C%20on%20another%20and%20more%20personal%20note%2C%20he%20most%20recently%20co-authored%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Delightful%20Mr.%20Daphtary%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0on%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20Solicitor%20General%2C%20C.K.%20Daphtary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20will%20be%20written%20on%20this%20great%20jurist%E2%80%99s%20contributions%20to%20the%20bar%2C%20the%20bench%2C%20and%20the%20nation.%20But%20to%20me%2C%20Fali%20will%20always%20remain%20the%20conscience%20keeper.%20%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERest%20in%20peace%2C%20Fali.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EChander%20Uday%20Singh%20is%20a%20Senior%20Advocate.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%