%3A%2Fwww.idu.org%2Fmembers%2F%5C%22%3ENovember%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20BJP%20was%20conspicuously%20absent%20from%20the%20members%E2%80%99%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reached%20out%20to%20the%20IDU%20to%20inquire%20about%20the%20current%20membership%20status%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%2C%20if%20not%20a%20member%2C%20the%20rationale%20behind%20their%20departure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20emailed%20reply%2C%20the%20secretary%20general%20of%20IDU%2C%20Tina%20Mercep%2C%20replied%20that%20the%20IDU%20%E2%80%9Cenjoys%20a%20warm%20and%20open%20dialogue%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20would%20welcome%20full%20membership%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20our%20global%20network%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMercep%2C%20a%20Croatian%20politician%2C%20also%20wrote%20that%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20youth%20organisation%20remains%20a%20member%20of%20the%20youth%20wing%20of%20the%20IDU.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20IDU%2C%20the%20member%20political%20parties%20profess%20the%20%E2%80%9Cideals%20of%20liberal%20democracy%2C%20freedom%20of%20the%20individual%2C%20and%20the%20need%20for%20economic%20growth%20to%20be%20based%20on%20individual%20initiative%20and%20free%2C%20competitive%20enterprise%20economies%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20it%20says%20that%20through%20the%20IDU%2C%20the%20members%20could%20%E2%80%9Cexchange%20policy%20ideas%2C%20assist%20each%20other%20to%20win%20the%20political%20argument%2C%20and%20to%20win%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708514066000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F30161148%2F406110211_773446158163006_4756603232278021214_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-conspicuous-by-absence-from-global-centre-right-political-parties-alliance%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20BJP%20has%20not%20been%20among%20the%20members%20of%20International%20Democracy%20Union%20for%20at%20least%20six%20months%20now%2C%20the%20Munich-based%20organisation%20has%20said%20it%20is%20happy%20to%20welcome%20BJP%20return%20to%20'full%20membership'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-conspicuous-by-absence-from-global-centre-right-political-parties-alliance%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22At%20a%20Time%20When%20the%20Battles%20of%20India's%20Future%20Will%20Be%20Fought%20in%20its%20Courts%2C%20We%20Will%20Miss%20Fali%20Nariman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21155108%2FUntitled-design-2-4.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFali%20Nariman%20is%20no%20more%20and%20the%20legal%20profession%20will%20never%20be%20the%20same%20again.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20there%20is%20no%20need%20to%20fear%20change%2C%20a%20part%20of%20our%20living%20history%20is%20lost.%20This%20is%20a%20very%20important%20part%2C%20which%20began%20before%20the%20constitution%20came%20into%20force%20and%20which%20continues%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Fali%20Nariman%20was%20a%20man%20who%20saw%20the%20making%20and%20unmaking%20of%20the%20constitution.%20Acutely%20conscious%20of%20an%20attack%20on%20secular%20values%20he%20spoke%20up%20defending%20his%20liberal%20values%20and%20continued%20doing%20so%2C%20almost%20till%20his%20last%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20a%20liberal%20in%20the%20constitutional%20sense%20of%20the%20word%2C%20defending%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20citizens%20against%20an%20overbearing%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Belonging%20as%20he%20did%20to%20a%20minority%20community%2C%20he%20was%20also%20aware%20of%20the%20constitutional%20commitment%20to%20minorities%20in%20this%20country%2C%20a%20country%20which%20gave%20him%20the%20opportunity%20to%20rise%20to%20the%20top%20of%20his%20profession%20and%20to%20serve%20it%20in%20turn.%20He%20was%20shaped%20by%20the%20city%20of%20Bombay%2C%20now%20Mumbai%2C%20which%20enabled%20him%20to%20represent%20big%20businesses%20and%20master%20commercial%20law.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20commitment%20to%20democracy%20was%20obvious%20when%20he%20resigned%20as%20Solicitor%20General%20of%20India%20in%201975%20upon%20the%20declaration%20of%20the%20Emergency.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20legal%20profession%20owes%20him%20a%20lot%2C%20but%20primarily%20the%20fact%20that%20he%20fought%20for%20and%20sought%20the%20collegium%20system%20of%20appointing%20judges.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%2C%20during%20his%20lifetime%2C%20challenged%20every%20law%20which%20attempted%20to%20give%20governments%20the%20dominant%20voice%20or%20the%20last%20word%20in%20appointing%20judges%20to%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20and%20high%20courts.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20stood%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20the%20separation%20of%20powers%20between%20the%20executive%20and%20the%20judiciary.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20big%20question%20is%2C%20will%20generations%20that%20follow%20%E2%80%93%20particularly%20the%20young%20lawyers%20of%20today%20%E2%80%93%20be%20able%20to%20ensure%20this%20separation%20of%20the%20domain%20of%20justice%20from%20the%20domain%20of%20partisan%20politics%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20he%20leaves%20a%20legacy%2C%20it%20is%20this%3A%20without%20independence%20of%20the%20judiciary%20from%20the%20executive%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20constitution%20will%20be%20reduced%20to%20nothing%20more%20than%20a%20piece%20of%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELoud%20and%20aggressive%20in%20his%20advocacy%20of%20a%20case%20or%20a%20cause%2C%20Fali%20Nariman%20saw%20this%20country%20change%20from%20a%20colony%20to%20an%20independent%20state.%20He%20also%20saw%20it%20through%20the%20Emergency%20of%201975%20and%20watched%20it%20arrive%20at%20this%20post-2014%20state%2C%20which%20calls%20into%20question%20the%20basic%20features%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20where%20India%20is%20described%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98temple%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFali%20Nariman%20did%20what%20one%20individual%20could%20do%20in%20a%20lifetime%20and%20more%2C%20leaving%20behind%20a%20challenge%20for%20the%20lawyers%20of%20today%20to%20carry%20the%20defence%20of%20the%20constitution%20forward.%20At%20a%20time%20when%20the%20battles%20of%20the%20future%20will%20be%20in%20the%20courts%2C%20we%20will%20miss%20him.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndira%20Jaising%20is%20a%20noted%20human%20rights%20lawyer%20and%20a%20senior%20advocate%20at%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708512809000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21155108%2FUntitled-design-2-4.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffali-nariman-obituary-indira-jaising%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22He%20was%20a%20liberal%20in%20the%20constitutional%20sense%20of%20the%20word%2C%20defending%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20of%20citizens%20against%20an%20overbearing%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Ffali-nariman-obituary-indira-jaising%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Great%20Crossover%3A%20Opposition%20Leaders%20Who%20Joined%20the%20BJP%20After%20Action%20by%20Central%20Agencies%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F21143240%2FCopy-of-Copy-of-Lead-image-size-10.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EMumbai%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20week%20ago%2C%20addressing%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20the%20Congress%20Maharashtra%20in-charge%20Ramesh%20Chennithala%20said%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cwashing%20machine%E2%80%9D%20and%20any%20opposition%20leader%20facing%20an%20investigation%20by%20central%20agencies%20like%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20or%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20%E2%80%93%20and%20willing%20to%20hop%20over%20to%20the%20other%20side%20%E2%80%93%20is%20readily%20accepted%20in%20the%20BJP.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20in%20Karnataka%2C%20chief%20minister%20Siddaramaiah%20called%20the%20central%20agencies%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20affiliates%E2%80%9D%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20called%20the%20agencies%20%E2%80%9CBJP%E2%80%99s%20jawans%E2%80%9D.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhat%20Chennithala%2C%20Siddaramaiah%20or%20Kharge%20said%20is%20not%20new.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20coinages%20have%20gained%20wide%20popularity%20in%20the%20recent%20years%2C%20as%20many%20leaders%20from%20the%20opposition%20have%20jumped%20ship%20and%20joined%20either%20the%20BJP%20or%20its%20ally%20parties%20fearing%20adverse%20action%20against%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20put%20together%20a%20state-wise%20list%20of%20politicians%20who%20have%20joined%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20past%20several%20months%20while%20facing%20criminal%20charges%20by%20the%20central%20agencies.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20a%20comprehensive%20list%3B%20in%20fact%2C%20even%20as%20we%20put%20it%20together%2C%20many%20leaders%20from%20the%20opposition%20camp%20might%20actually%20be%20on%20their%20way%20to%20a%20nearby%20BJP%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMaharashtra%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBhavana%20Gawali%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%202020%2C%20the%20ED%20accused%20Gawali%2C%20the%20member%20of%20parliament%20from%20Yavatmal-Washim%20constituency%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20of%20alleged%20misappropriation%20of%20Rs%207%20crore%20from%20a%20public%20trust%2C%20Mahila%20Utkarsha%20Pratisthan%2C%20where%20Gawali%20was%20chairperson.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20few%20months%20later%2C%20the%20ED%20arrested%20her%20close%20aide%2C%20Saeed%20Khan.%20In%20late%202021%20and%202022%2C%20Gawali%20was%20summoned%20multiple%20times%20to%20the%20ED%20office%20for%20an%20inquiry.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20ED%20filed%20a%20chargesheet%20in%20the%20case%20and%20named%20five%20persons.%20The%20public%20trust%20linked%20to%20Gawali%20was%20also%20mentioned%20in%20the%20ED%20chargesheet.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20July%202022%2C%20however%2C%20Gawali%20decided%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction.%20She%20was%20soon%20announced%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20chief%20whip%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ED%20case%3F%20There%20have%20been%20no%20developments%20since%20then.%20Neither%20has%20the%20ED%20filed%20a%20supplementary%20chargesheet%20nor%20has%20Gawali%20been%20summoned%20for%20further%20inquiries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EPratap%20Sarnaik%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20June%202021%2C%20while%20still%20with%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Sarnaik%20had%20written%20to%20Thackeray%20asking%20him%20to%20patch%20things%20up%20with%20the%20BJP.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20will%20save%20the%20party%20of%20the%20harassment%20by%20central%20investigation%20agencies%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Ovala-Majiwada%20constituency%20MLA%20had%20claimed%20in%20the%20letter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESarnaik%20and%20his%20family%2C%20at%20that%20time%2C%20were%20facing%20an%20ED%20investigation%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20National%20Spot%20Exchange%20Limited%20(NSEL)%20scam%20worth%20Rs%205%2C600%20crore.%20The%20ED%20had%20questioned%20him%20and%20had%20also%20taken%20into%20possession%20112%20plots%20belonging%20to%20his%20firm.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20June%202022%2C%20as%20Eknath%20Shinde%20decided%20to%20rebel%20against%20the%20Thackeray%20camp%20and%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Sarnaik%20was%20one%20of%20the%20first%20ones%20to%20jump%20ship.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInterestingly%2C%20this%20case%20was%20first%20handled%20by%20the%20state%20Economic%20Offences%20Wing%20(EOW)%20which%20had%20filed%20a%20closure%20report%20while%20Thackeray%20was%20the%20state%20chief%20minister.%20But%20the%20ED%20had%20eventually%20taken%20over%20the%20case.%20Once%20Sarnaik%20went%20along%20with%20the%20Shinde%20faction%2C%20the%20ED%2C%20as%20expected%2C%20slowed%20its%20investigation%20down.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHasan%20Mushrif%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%20March%202023%2C%20the%20ED%20conducted%20searches%20at%20Mushrif%E2%80%99s%20residence%20and%20offices%20in%20Mumbai%20and%20Kolhapur%20in%20connection%20with%20an%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case.%20BJP%20leader%20Kirit%20Somaiya%20had%20alleged%20that%20Mushrif%20had%20misappropriated%20funds%20in%20the%20Sar%20Senapati%20Santaji%20Ghorpade%20Sugar%20Mill%2C%20Appasaheb%20Nalwade%20Gadhinlaj%20Taluka%20Cooperative%20Sugar%20Mill%20and%20the%20running%20of%20the%20Kolhapur%20District%20Central%20Cooperative%20Bank%2C%20of%20which%20Mushrif%20is%20the%20chairman.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMusrif%20had%20to%20move%20the%20court%20which%20granted%20him%20interim%20relief%20but%20his%20arrest%20seemed%20inevitable%20at%20that%20time.%20But%20in%20July%202023%2C%20as%20Ajit%20Pawar%20decided%20to%20break%20the%20National%20Congress%20Party%20(NCP)%20party%20and%20join%20hands%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20Musrif%20went%20too.%20Since%20then%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20news%20on%20any%20further%20investigation%20or%20raids%20at%20his%20residence.%20The%20case%2C%20however%2C%20is%20pending%20in%20the%20court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EYamini%20Jadhav%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20prominent%20Sena%20MLA%20and%20wife%20of%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20Brihanmumbai%20Municipal%20Corporation%20(BMC)%E2%80%99s%20Standing%20Committee%20Yashwant%20Jadhav%20too%20has%20been%20facing%20ED%20charges%20in%20an%20alleged%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA)%20violations%20case.%20In%20April%202022%2C%20the%20IT%20department%20attached%2041%20properties%20belonging%20to%20the%20couple%20and%20the%20ED%20summoned%20both%20her%20and%20her%20husband%20for%20inquiry.%20Later%2C%20Jadhav%20joined%20the%20Shinde%20camp%20and%20things%20have%20since%20been%20quiet%20for%20the%20couple.%20In%20July%202022%2C%20when%20Jadhav%20registered%20her%20head%20count%20for%20the%20Speaker%E2%80%99s%20election%20in%20the%20assembly%20as%20an%20MLA%20belonging%20to%20the%20Shinde%20camp%2C%20the%20members%20on%20the%20opposition%20benches%20shouted%20%E2%80%9CED%2C%20ED%E2%80%9D%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20reasons%20for%20her%20and%20many%20other%20party%20members%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20quit%20the%20Thackeray%20faction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChhagan%20Bhujbal%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20senior%20NCP%20leader%20and%20a%20strong%20OBC%20face%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Bhujbal%20decided%20to%20switch%20sides%20and%20go%20with%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP.%20Bhujbal%20has%20been%20facing%20inquiries%20in%20the%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20awarding%20of%20contracts%20of%20over%20Rs%20100%20crore%20for%20three%20projects%20in%202006%20when%20he%20was%20the%20state%20PWD%20minister.%20He%20was%20also%20booked%20in%20another%20alleged%20money%20laundering%20case%20by%20the%20ED%20and%2C%20in%202016%2C%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fncp-leader-chhagan-bhujbal-arrested-by-ed-in-money-laundering-case-313247-2016-03-14%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Earrested%20by%20the%20central%20agency%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlthough%20Bhujbal%20went%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20he%20has%20been%20openly%20expressing%20his%20discontent%20but%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20shown%20the%20courage%20to%20quit%20the%20party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAshok%20Chavan%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20senior%20Congress%20leader%20and%20two-time%20chief%20minister%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Chavan%20announced%20that%20he%20too%20is%20joining%20the%20BJP%20earlier%20this%20month.%20While%20he%20gave%20no%20reasons%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20the%2065-year-old%20MLA%20from%20Nanded%20has%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fashok-chavan-adarsh-scam-congress-bjp%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Efacing%20a%20CBI%20probe%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20over%20a%20decade%20and%20half.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20and%20his%20family%20members%20are%20accused%20of%20being%20primary%20beneficiaries%20of%20a%2031-storey%20building%20named%20Adarsh%20Co-operative%20Housing%20Society%20which%20was%20originally%20built%20for%201999%20Kargil%20war%20heroes%20and%20fallen%20soldiers%E2%80%99%20war%20widows.%20The%20ED%20too%20is%20investigating%20the%20matter%20and%20Chavan%20has%20been%20named%20as%20an%20accused.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20ordered%20a%20stay%20in%20the%20proceedings%20in%202018.%20The%20trial%20in%20the%20CBI%20case%20is%20yet%20to%20begin.%20The%20ED%2C%20meanwhile%20has%20not%20proceeded%20with%20arrests%20or%20filed%20a%20chargesheet.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBaba%20Siddiqui%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20In%202017%2C%20the%20ED%20conducted%20raids%20at%20the%20premises%20linked%20to%20Siddiqui%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20money%20laundering%20case%20over%20a%20land%20deal%20related%20to%20a%20slum%20rehabilitation%20project.%20The%20three-time%20MLA%20from%20Mumbai%E2%80%99s%20Bandra%20had%20allegedly%20misused%20his%20position%20as%20chairman%20of%20the%20Mumbai%20board%20of%20The%20Maharashtra%20Housing%20and%20Area%20Development%20Authority%20(MHADA)%20between%202000-2004%20and%20allowed%20irregularities%20re-development%20of%20a%20slum%20at%20Bandra%20in%20suburban%20Mumbai.%20Siddiqui%2C%20according%20to%20the%20ED%20was%20a%20direct%20beneficiary.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20case%20is%20pending%2C%20the%20ED%20has%20slowed%20down%20action%20against%20Siddiqui.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20Siddiqui%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20party%20to%20join%20Ajit%20Pawar%E2%80%99s%20NCP.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAjit%20Pawar%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20A%20senior%20NCP%20leader%2C%20who%20shocked%20the%20party%20by%20suddenly%20deciding%20to%20break%20ties%20with%20his%20uncle%20and%20party%20founder%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20Ajit%20Pawar%20is%20not%20new%20to%20controversies.%20Ajit%20has%20been%20facing%20cases%20filed%20by%20multiple%20agencies%20%E2%80%93%20both%20on%20the%20state%20and%20central%20level.%20These%20cases%20%E2%80%93%20pertaining%20to%20a%20co-operative%20bank%20and%20the%20state%20irrigation%20project%20%E2%80%93%20has%20dragged%20on%20for%20close%20to%20a%20decade.%20The%20action%2C%20however%2C%20has%20always%20been%20dependent%20on%20the%20party%20in%20power.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20EOW%20first%20accused%20Pawar%20of%20allowing%20irregularities%20in%20loans%20given%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20State%20Cooperative%20Bank.%20Based%20on%20this%20investigation%20by%20the%20EOW%2C%20the%20ED%20too%20filed%20a%20case%20of%20money%20laundering%20against%20him.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20the%20MahaVikas%20Aghadi%20came%20to%20power%20in%202019%2C%20the%20EOW%20case%20suddenly%20lost%20steam%20and%20the%20agency%20told%20the%20court%20that%20no%20evidence%20was%20found%20against%20him.%20A%20closure%20report%20was%20filed%20before%20a%20special%20court.%20The%20ED%20investigation%2C%20however%2C%20continued.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20Ajit%20was%20the%20water%20resources%20minister%20in%20the%20Congress-NCP%20government%20and%20chairman%20of%20the%20Vidarbha%20Irrigation%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20he%20was%20accused%20of%20allowing%20irregularities%20in%20the%20irrigation%20projects.%20Based%20on%20PILs%2C%20the%20Maharashtra%20Anti%20Corruption%20Branch%20(ACB)%20began%20a%20court-monitored%20investigation%20in%20this%20regard.%20This%20case%20again%20was%20kept%20in%20cold%20storage%20and%20in%202019%2C%20a%20day%20after%20he%20formed%20the%20short-lived%20government%20with%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20the%20ACB%20sprung%20a%20surprise%20by%20submitting%20a%20report%20before%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%20giving%20him%20a%20clean%20chit.%20The%20report%2C%20however%2C%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20accepted%20by%20the%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EGoa%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EDigambar%20Kamat%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20infamous%20Louis%20Berger%20case%20involves%20water%20management%20projects%20taken%20up%20in%20Assam%20and%20Goa.%20Former%20chief%20minister%20Digambar%20Kamat%20and%20former%20state%20public%20works%20department%20minister%20Churchill%20Alemao%20were%20accused%20in%20the%20bribery%20case.%20It%20was%20first%20handled%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20the%20ED%20came%20in%20to%20picture%20soon%20after.%20According%20to%20the%20FIR%2C%2014%20shell%20companies%20had%20ferried%20bribes%20worth%20crores%20of%20rupees%20from%20the%20New%20Jersey-based%20consultancy%20Louis%20Berger%20to%20politicians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20and%20the%20investigation%20that%20started%20sometime%20in%202015%20against%20Kamat%20and%20others%2C%20intensified%20in%202021.%20In%20September%202022%2C%20Kamat%2C%20along%20with%20either%20other%20Congress%20MLAs%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAndhra%20Pradesh%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EC.M.%20Ramesh%20and%20Y.S.%20Chowdary%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20two%20of%20the%20four%20Telegu%20Desam%20Party%20Rajya%20Sabha%20members%20who%20crossed%20over%20to%20the%20BJP%20in%20June%202021%2C%20are%20also%20industrialists%20and%20have%20been%20under%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Ftdp-mps-joins-bjp-two-face-cbi-ed-it-probes-mallyas-5791624%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Escanner%20of%20IT%2C%20CBI%20and%20ED%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMonths%20before%20they%20joined%20the%20saffron%20party%2C%20BJP%20MP%20and%20spokesperson%20G.V.L.%20Narasimha%20Rao%20had%20called%20both%20Chowdary%20and%20Ramesh%20%E2%80%9CAndhra%20Mallyas%E2%80%9D.%20Rao%20had%20also%20written%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Ethics%20Committee%2C%20seeking%20initiation%20of%20%E2%80%9Csuitable%20action%E2%80%9D%20against%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMost%20recently%2C%20both%20AP%20chief%20minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fed-court-summons-jagan-in-land-allotments-case%2Farticleshow%2F80195476.cms%5C%22%3EY.S.%20Jagan%20Mohan%20Reddy%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20former%20chief%20minister%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fchandrababu-naidu-arrested-what-is-andhra-pradesh-skill-development-corruption-case-explained-11694228555687.html%5C%22%3EChandrababu%20Naidu%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20who%20are%20facing%20multiple%20cases%20of%20corruption%20have%20begun%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thequint.com%2Felections%2Fandhra-pradesh-election%2Fchandrababu-naidu-jagan-mohan-reddy-bjp-andhra-pradesh-alliance%23read-more%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecosying%20up%20with%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20While%20the%20cases%20against%20R