ring%20determination.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COn%20the%20risk%20of%20sounding%20too%20unrealistic%2C%20I%20want%20to%20emphasise%20that%20at%20the%20time%20of%20renovating%20the%20school%2C%20I%20had%20nothing%20but%20a%20passion%20towards%20education.%20The%20school%20had%20under%2023%20students%20back%20then%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20more%20than%20100%2C%E2%80%9D%20Gopal%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20students%20at%20the%20Integrated%20Middle%20School%20in%20Mohanpura%20Colony%20was%20made%20possible%20after%20Gopal%20took%20on%20the%20mission%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285414%2Fgerman-teacher-starts-ngo-renovate-kerala-anganwadis-helps-bring-girls-to-school%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erenovating%20the%20school.%20%3C%2Fa%3ETowards%20this%2C%20he%20spent%20Rs%203%20lakh%20from%20his%20own%20pocket%2C%20using%20which%20he%20revamped%20the%20walls%20and%20washrooms%2C%20planted%20a%20garden%2C%20brought%20water%20to%20the%20school%2C%20and%20set%20up%20a%20library.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20a%20neglected%20school%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gopal%20was%20assigned%20to%20the%20middle%20school%2C%20what%20greeted%20him%20were%20a%20handful%20of%20students%20and%20four%20poorly%20lit%20classrooms%20masquerading%20as%20a%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20school%20was%20in%20a%20deplorable%20state%2C%20to%20put%20it%20mildly.%20The%20walls%20lacked%20paint%2C%20and%20there%20was%20a%20noticeable%20lack%20of%20enthusiasm%20in%20the%20students%E2%80%99%20eyes%2C%20which%20troubled%20me%20the%20most.%20However%2C%20I%20could%20empathise%20because%20even%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20study%20in%20such%20conditions%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopal%20explains%20that%20most%20of%20the%20students%20and%20residents%20hailed%20from%20villages%20near%20the%20Mohanpura%20Dam.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20construction%20of%20the%20dam%20forced%20these%20people%20to%20relocate.%20The%20Government%20built%20a%20few%20houses%20and%20roads%2C%20and%20labelled%20it%20Mohanpura%20Colony.%20However%20they%20did%20not%20create%20any%20employment%20for%20the%20people%20displaced%20who%20had%20lost%20their%20lands%20and%20had%20no%20avenue%20of%20income.%20So%20most%20of%20the%20people%20were%20worried%20about%20bringing%20food%20to%20the%20table%20at%20the%20time%2C%20and%20educational%20concerns%20were%20far%20from%20being%20in%20their%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Old%20school%20(top%20right)%20and%20the%20newly%20transformed%20school%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fschool-8-1708436803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342503%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOld%20school%20(top%20right)%20and%20the%20newly%20transformed%20school.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20continues%2C%20%E2%80%9CAlso%20while%20setting%20up%20the%20colony%20for%20the%20people%2C%20the%20villagers%20were%20given%20a%20broken-down