edes%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20says%20cheekily.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EAround%20the%20world%20in%2076%20days%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20child%2C%20Daman%20never%20saw%20Lal%20Pari%20as%20a%20car.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20mother%20would%20tell%20me%20these%20stories%20of%20how%20Lal%20Pari%20had%20superpowers%20and%20could%20come%20to%20save%20us%20whenever%20we%20needed.%20I%20grew%20up%20believing%20that.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20my%20favourite%20memories%20have%20been%20in%20this%20car%2C%E2%80%9D%20Daman%20adds.%20These%20include%20trips%20to%20the%20zoo%20when%20he%20was%20younger%2C%20family%20trips%20when%20he%20was%20older%2C%20and%20eventually%20his%20marriage.%20So%2C%20it%20only%20seemed%20right%20that%20the%20car%20was%20his%20companion%20on%20this%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F338637%2Fmeghalaya-homestay-travellers-nest-vacation-adventure-lovers-mawlyngbna-caving-canyoning-treks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edreamy%20adventure%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENavigating%20across%20the%20world%20on%20an%20impulse%20and%20high%20adrenaline%20means%20figuring%20out%20where%20your%20next%20lunch%20is%20going%20to%20be%2C%20hoping%20to%20find%20a%20petrol%20pump%20in%20a%20remote%20village%20where%20water%20is%20gold%2C%20and%20driving%20towards%20the%20next%20destination%20with%20hope%2C%20even%20when%20the%20road%20gets%20tough.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20through%20it%20all%2C%20Lal%20Pari%20was%20very%20well-behaved.%20Before%20embarking%20on%20this%20daring%20tryst%2C%20only%20the%20carburettor%20was%20changed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBetter%20fuel%20efficiency%20and%20more%20reliability%2C%20you%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20car%2C%20the%20engine%2C%20the%20gearbox%2C%20and%20the%20decor%20were%20preserved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEvery%20dawn