4%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20district%20is%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FKatni-1708432131-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-342448%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20district%20is%20providing%20rations%20worth%20Rs%20600%20per%20child%20every%20month.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%2C%20the%20IAS%20officer%20says%2C%20has%20brought%20people%20from%20all%20walks%20of%20life%20and%20groups%20%E2%80%94%20including%20industrialists%2C%20doctors%2C%20non-profit%20organisations%2C%20and%20individuals%20%E2%80%94%20to%20join%20the%20nutrition%20campaign%20of%20the%20district%20administration.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20programme%20kicked%20off%20in%20January%202023%2C%20there%20were%20232%20SAM%20and%201%2C318%20MAM%20children%20in%20the%20district.%20Within%20a%20year%2C%20the%20nutrition%20campaign%20resulted%20in%20an%20improvement%20of%2027%20percent%20and%2023%20percent%20in%20the%20nutrition%20level%20of%20SAM%20and%20MAM%20children%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20phase%20of%20the%20programme%2C%20the%20district%20was%20able%20to%20adopt%20around%20600%20malnourished%20children.%20But%20we%20still%20have%20at%20least%201%2C000%20malnourished%20children%20in%20our%20district.%20Of%20these%2C%2050%20are%20severely%20