are%20grown%20and%20which%20variety%20survives.%20Now%2C%20I%20earn%20more%20than%20Rs%201%20lakh%20a%20month%20by%20selling%20lilies%20during%20a%20good%20season%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EViji%20shares%20the%20secrets%20behind%20her%20healthy%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F208990%2Fsustainable-garden-green-peace-home-garden-indoor-plants-garden-workshops-char01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreen%20garden%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20how%20you%20too%20can%20grow%20water%20lilies%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EJourney%20to%20her%20magic%20garden%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERaised%20with%20an%20affinity%20for%20plants%20and%20greenery%2C%20Viji%20has%20been%20fond%20of%20gardening%20for%20most%20of%20her%20life.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20must%20have%20been%20decades%20since%20I%20have%20been%20tending%20to%20a%20garden.%20It%20is%20my%20favourite%20thing%20to%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20becoming%20a%20full-time%20gardener%2C%20she%20was%20an%20accountant.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20sounds%20like%20two%20different%20worlds%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20gardening%20was%20always%20a%20part%20of%20who%20I%20was.%20When%20my%20first%20child%20was%20born%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20lived%20on%20our%20own.%20So%20one%20of%20us%20had%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F313207%2Faravinthan-coimbatore-organic-farm-seed-bank-preserves-rare-varieties-vegetables-pulses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Equit%20our%20job%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20raise%20the%20children.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20I%20decided%20to%20leave%20my%20job%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20putting%20down%20her%20papers%2C%20Viji%E2%80%99s%20mind%20was%20not%20at%20ease.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20wanted%20to%20create%20and%20leave%20back%20something%20of%20my%20own%20i