82%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20100%20percent%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20working%20in%20the%20renewable%20energy%20sector%2C%20Amit%20wanted%20to%20work%20towards%20addressing%20India%E2%80%99s%20energy%20crises.%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20a%20fast-growing%20country%2C%20which%20is%20also%20increasing%20the%20use%20of%20fossil%20fuels.%20Since%20the%20country%20is%20significantly%20dependent%20on%20imports%20for%20its%20energy%20needs%2C%20there%20is%20a%20very%20strong%20business%20sense%20for%20harnessing%20the%20power%20of%20green%20hydrogen%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2039-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20why%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CSome%20of%20the%20major%20factors%20why%20we%20feel%20India%20needs%20green%20hydrogen%20include%2C%20energy%20independence%2C%20achieving%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20net%20zero%20targets%2C%20and%20creating%20huge%20job%20opportunities.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20expected%20to%20save%20our%20forex.%20The%20precious%20foreign%20exchange%20saved%20by%20reducing%20fossil%20fuel%20imports%20can%20be%20harnessed%20for%20social%20use%20such%20as%20health%20and%20education.%20Further%2C%20the%20country%20can%20even%20target%20to%20become%20a%20net%20exporter%20of%20ammonia%20and%20its%20derivatives%20from%20being%20a%20large%20importer%20of%20fossil%20fuels%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20Amit%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CGreen%20hydrogen%20and%20its%20derivatives%20as%20fuel%20can%20decarbonise%20hard-to-abate%20sectors%2C%20especially%20since%20these%20sectors%20contribute%20nearly%2080%20percent%20of%20carbon%20footprint.%20This%20will%20be%20crucial%20as%20conventional%20electricity%20replacement%20by%20100%20percent%20green%20electricity%20will%20only%20result%20in%2020%20percent%20decarbonisation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20the%20most%20of%20a%20growing%20demand%20for%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Amit%20launched%20Hygenco%20in%202020%20with%20a%20vision%20to%20help%20India%20achieve%20energy%20independence%2C%20especially%20as%20the%20climate%20challenges%20continue%20to%20rise%2C%20and%20ensure%20a%20sustainable%20future%20for%20the%20coming%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hygenco%20Green%20Energies%20signed%20a%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20long-term%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Limited.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FOdisha-4-1707917279-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-341877%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EHygenco%20Green%20Energies%20signed%20green%20hydrogen%20and%20green%20oxygen%20long-term%20offtake%20agreement%20with%20Sterlite%20Technologies%20Limited.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20step%20closer%20towards%20green%20solutions%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmit%20continues%20to%20inform%20that%20Hygenco%20builds%2C%20owns%2C%20and%20operates%20multiple%20green%20hydrogen%20facilities%20across%20the%20country%2C%20including%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20one%20of%20the%20few%20companies%20offering%20comprehensive%20360-degree%20techno-commercial%20solutions%20utilising%20green%20hydrogen.%20We%20offer%20cost-competitive%20alternatives%20for%20sustainable%20transportation.%20We%20are%20not%20just%20building%20infrastructure%3B%20we%20are%20shaping%20the%20future%20of%20clean%20energy%20and%20transportation%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20plants%20are%20designed%20with%20ambitious%20sustainability%20targets%20with%20the%20primary%20goal%20to%20responsibly%20conserve%20and%20source%20water%20for%20all%20our%20projects.%20With%20plants%20incorporating%20advanced%20software%20stack%2C%20Hygenco%E2%80%99s%20innovative%20approach%20enables%20efficiently%20consuming%20renewable%20power%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Amit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20its%20commitment%20towards%20leveraging%20green%20hydrogen%2C%20Hygenco%20has%20entered%20into%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20long-term%20green%20hydrogen%20purchase%20agreement%20with%20Jindal%20Stainless%20Limited%20(JSL).%20The%20project%20is%20a%20state-of-the-art%20green%20hydrogen%20facility%20located%20at%20JSL%20steel%20plant%20in%20Hisar%20that%20has%20a%20target%20to%20reduce%20carbon%20emissions%20considerably%20by%20about%202%2C700%20metric%20tonnes%20per%20annum.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20plant%20is%20expected%20to%20produce%2075%20tonnes%20per%20annum%20of%20green%20hydrogen%20using%20roof-top%20and%20floating%20solar%20energy%20sources%20installed%20within%20the%20factory%20premises%2C%20contributing%20towards%20reducing%20carbon%20footprint%20and%20building%20a%20sustainable%20eco-system.%20With%20this%2C%20Hygenco%20will%20run%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20commercial%20long%20term%20offtake%20green%20hydrogen%20plant%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another